Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.03,0:38:07.78,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}小心槳端\NMind your oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.47,0:38:11.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拉姆斯德爾 準備繩 是 長官\N- Mr. Ramsdell, prepare the line. - Aye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.27,0:38:16.89,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}第一頭是我的\NThe first one's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.49,0:38:20.16,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}瞄準她的弱點\NAim her to the free spot!
