Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.33,0:38:45.43,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}夥計們 你們坐上了楠塔基特號第一班雪橇\NYou're on your first Nantucket sleigh ride, Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.38,0:39:02.50,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}地球上最可怕的生物\NThe most fearsome creature to ever live on this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.68,0:39:18.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我的手\NMy hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.16,0:39:28.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你得把繩弄濕 尼克森\NYou need to wet the line, Nickerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.85,0:39:43.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}只剩140英尋的繩子了 查斯先生\NA hundred forty fathoms' of line left, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.37,0:39:54.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}只剩80英尋的繩子了 長官\NEighty fathoms' of line left, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.74,0:40:01.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他會把我們拖到水裏的\NHe's gonna pull us under!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.56,0:40:06.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}馬修 我要你的繩子 給我繩\N- Matthew, I need your line! - Feed the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.39,0:40:08.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}彼得森給我繩子 是的 長官\N- Peterson give me the line! - Aye, Sir.
