Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.52,0:40:18.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}20英尋了 查斯先生 鬆開繩\N- Twenty fathoms, Mr. Chase! - Tie it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.72,0:40:24.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}快\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.01,0:40:39.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}彼得森 你來 是 長官\N- Peterson, lay on! - Aye, Sir.
