Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.59,0:41:04.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}歐文 他媽的 我說了不要動\N- Owen! God damn it! - I said don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.57,0:41:05.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}剩30英尋了 花花公子\NThirty fathoms left, Mr. Joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.68,0:41:12.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}剩10英尋了 長官\NTen fathoms left, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.20,0:42:38.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}真是漫長的過程\NIt's been a long drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.99,0:42:57.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}油中的脂肪\NBlubber in the oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.87,0:43:00.20,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}它們要吃掉你的錢了\NThey're gonna eat your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.30,0:43:02.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}滾開 混賬畜生\NGet out of there, you sons of bitches!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.94,0:43:08.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}- 你拿到了嗎 拿到了 查斯\N- You got it? - Got it, Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.09,0:43:13.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}看起來怎麼樣 不怎麼樣\N- How's it lookin'? - Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.38,0:43:17.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}就這麼多了\NThat's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.46,0:43:23.95,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生 什麼\N- Mr. Chase, Sir? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.00,0:43:26.38,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}長官 就這麼多了 我們拿不到更多了\NThat's all of it, Sir, we can't get anymore out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.50,0:43:29.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那就是金礦 夥計們 繼續挖\NThat's the gold in there, Boys, c'mon, keep diggin'.
