Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.64,0:43:40.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}尼克森 過來小子\NNickerson, come here boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.90,0:43:45.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿 我喊你過來\NHey! I said c'mere!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.37,0:43:50.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}爬進去\NClimb on in with 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.99,0:43:52.28,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}來啊 湯姆斯\NCome on, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.78,0:43:56.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這裏面的東西可比它的肉值錢多了\NWhat's in there is worth a HELLEVA lot more than what they're boilin' down.
