Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.83,0:44:14.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你用牙齒把這東西咬住 小子\NYou best put that between your teeth, Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.68,0:44:17.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}它裏面臭得很\NIt tastes worse than the Devil's asshole down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.01,0:44:22.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.50,0:44:31.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}抱歉 尼克森 我的枕頭送你\N- Sorry. - Here, Nickerson, take my pillow with ya!
