Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.17,0:44:54.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一個人在裏面能更瞭解自己\NA man gets to know himself down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.56,0:45:01.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們有送你進一頭鯨的頭裏面嗎 沒有 他們饒了我\N- Did they ever send you into a whale's head? - No, I was spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.86,0:45:04.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那裏面才是寶藏所在\NWell, that's where the treasure is.
