Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.37,0:45:15.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}47桶油 當然 幸福很短暫\NForty-seven barrels... of course, the happiness was short lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.32,0:45:17.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那片水域沒有鯨魚可捕了\NThe waters had all been fished out?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.91,0:45:23.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是的 所以我們向更遠處前進\NThat they had. So, we headed further out.
