Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.09,0:45:34.24,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}離開了南大西洋\NLeft the South Atlantic behind with a sliver of hope
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.29,0:45:36.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}期望情況會變好\Nthat things would change for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.28,0:45:41.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但到了太平洋事實上沒有改善\NBut making the Pacific didn't improve our lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.78,0:45:46.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}太他媽難看到鯨了\NWhale sightings were TOO damn scarce.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.80,0:45:52.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}將近一年後脾氣衝動的船長\NAfter nearly a year at sea the temperaments of our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.58,0:45:55.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}和大副都變的沮喪\NAnd our first mate grew more strained.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.13,0:46:00.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長波拉德幾乎整天待在船艙裏\NCaptain Pollard spent most days and nights in his cabin,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.89,0:46:03.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}害怕看到船員無法交代\Nafraid to look his crew in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.47,0:46:10.89,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們的倉儲大半還空著\NOur hold was almost empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.71,0:46:17.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}凝視著我們皮毛的成果只會提醒我們\NTo gaze upon our paltry efforts only served as a reminder
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.32,0:46:20.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}離回家還有很長一段路\Nthat we were a long way from going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.32,0:46:36.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}阿塔卡梅斯 厄瓜多爾
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.86,0:46:47.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我聽不懂 說英語\NI don't talk that talk. Speak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.95,0:46:53.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們在說鯨油\NThey're talking whale oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.95,0:47:17.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}牧師堅持要我們寫信回家告知我們的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.07,0:47:18.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他覺得這些信幫得了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.57,0:47:20.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那些寡婦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.57,0:47:21.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船都沒有的船主
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.87,0:47:25.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你還要像這樣生活多久 船長
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.07,0:47:33.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}寫信給西班牙 為你和你的船長 祈求原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.97,0:47:37.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒人可以阻止發生的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.57,0:47:41.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}誰會相信呢 沒有人 顧主不會相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.67,0:47:46.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這麼多年你用油換來錢裝滿他們的口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.29,0:47:49.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}長官\NCapitбn.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.09,0:47:53.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}打擾了 當地人告訴我你的航程遇到阻礙了 長官\NExcuse me, the locals told me that your voyage was waylaid, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.39,0:47:56.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號船長 喬治·波拉德\NCaptain George Pollard, the Essex.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.00,0:48:00.43,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}聖瑪麗亞號船長 克萊門特佩萊斯\NCapitбn Clemente Pelaez, the Santa Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.89,0:48:03.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}給大伙來一杯\NWould you buy a colleague a drink?
