Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.24,0:48:13.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}壞運氣\NBad luck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.36,0:48:16.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那有多遠\NHow far out?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.51,0:48:18.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}遠到只有傻子才會去\NFar enough for only a fool to go.
