Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.89,0:48:29.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}鯨都在那兒\NWere there whales there?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.40,0:48:32.09,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}多到你做夢不敢想\NMore than you've ever dreamt.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.69,0:48:36.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}成百上千 密密麻麻望不到邊\NHundreds... fields of flukes as far as the eye can see.
