Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.98,0:48:55.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}白如蠟石\NWhite as alabaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.28,0:48:57.05,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一百英尺長\Na hundred feet long,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.32,0:49:01.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我的六名船員因為它喪命\Nsent six of my crew to their graves,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.59,0:49:13.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}剩下的我們 只會讓人想起那頭怪物\Nand the rest of us, something to remember him by.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.30,0:49:18.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那頭白鯨 他跳舞給你看 還逗你玩嗎\NNow, this white whale, did he dance a jig and pick your pocket, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.33,0:49:25.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.37,0:49:29.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你相信他的鬼話\NDo you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.83,0:49:35.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們馬上出發 趕上南風帶\NWe set sail now, catch the south easterlies,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.92,0:49:39.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這是我們絕佳的機會 填飽肚子 我們有機會在半年內回家\Nthis is by our best time, fill our belly, we can be home in six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.21,0:49:42.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你怎麼看 查斯先生\NWhat say you, Mr. Chase?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.22,0:49:46.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒必要再忍受這種困境了\NNo need to endure our predicament for a moment longer than necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.62,0:49:47.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}同意\NAmen to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.05,0:49:50.34,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}同意\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.30,0:49:54.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}貪婪影響了船長和大副\NGreed took hold of our Captain and the first mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.30,0:49:59.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後我們沿著赤道前往一千里格外的\NSo, we headed out... a thousand leagues along the Equator...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.61,0:50:04.60,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是沒想到 傳言流開了\Nbut with no agenda, speculation began.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.41,0:50:07.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}說鯨都藏在那裏\NThis is where the whales are gonna hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.10,0:50:10.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那是我們能到達的最遠的地方\NIt was as far from land as we could possibly go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.42,0:50:13.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是我們要追捕他們\NBut we hunted them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.29,0:50:18.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}幾個世紀前 水手們害怕會航到地球邊界\NCenturies before, sailors feared sailing off the edge of the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.88,0:50:23.36,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但我們是駛向理智的邊緣\Nbut we were headed for the edge of sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.50,0:50:30.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}信任給猜疑讓位\NTrust gave way to doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.73,0:50:33.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}期望消除迷信\Nhope to blind superstition.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.97,0:50:36.09,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長 船員在議論\NCap'n, the men are talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.19,0:50:38.48,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這很正常\NThat's what men do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.53,0:50:41.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們對你航行這麼遠的決定不滿\NThey aren't happy with your decision to sail out this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.34,0:50:43.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你糾正他們的觀點了嗎\NWell, did you correct them?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.32,0:50:47.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你提醒他們我們的目標是用鯨油裝滿這艘船\NDid you remind them of our purpose to fill this ship with whale oil
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.15,0:50:50.24,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果那裏有成百上千頭鯨 為什麼不去呢\Nand if the whales ARE a thousand leagues out, then that is where we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.36,0:50:56.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}表哥 拜託了 這太瘋狂了\NCousin, please, this is madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.08,0:51:01.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你被那人影響了\NYou have let yourself be influenced by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.32,0:51:02.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你必須把船調頭\NYou must turn this ship back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.64,0:51:09.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我建議你回去 消除他們的疑慮\NI suggest you go back down, reassure the men, the leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.36,0:51:14.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}以後別再仗著家庭身份來找我\Nand don't ever, ever abuse the privilege of family with me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.65,0:51:18.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}克芬先生\NMr. Coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.65,0:51:31.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}出海第十四個月
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.40,0:51:49.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}怎麼了\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.47,0:51:52.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}聽 查斯先生\N- Listen... - Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.28,0:51:54.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我看到些白柱 哪裏\N- I see some white water. - Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.22,0:51:55.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}左舷\NPort side!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.26,0:51:59.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你看到什麼了嗎\NYou see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.18,0:52:09.38,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}出船 出船\N- Lower away! - Lower away!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.08,0:52:14.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那頭掛物要完蛋了\NThe Devil'll take the Mexican ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.07,0:53:01.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}用力刺他 刺他\NStick him hard! Stick him!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.45,0:53:07.28,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一直向前 彼得森\NStraight ahead, Peterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.78,0:53:20.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}別人他咬了船槳 夥計們\NDon't let him chew the oars, Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.98,0:53:22.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}看著點\NBack to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.98,0:53:48.71,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那頭鯨 是的\N- The whale? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.33,0:53:51.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}傳言是真的 是的\N- So, it's true. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.38,0:53:53.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}可惜是真的\NToo much is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.98,0:54:13.45,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}全速\NFull pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.63,0:54:31.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}邦德先生 後退4碼 載具放下來\NMr. Bond, back to 4 yards, lower the tackle!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.07,0:54:33.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}遵命 長官\NAye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.99,0:54:53.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}勞倫斯先生 駛向下風口的鯨群\NMr. Lawrence, take us leeward headed straight for the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.17,0:54:53.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}馬上 長官\NRight, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.11,0:54:56.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}熱焦油 長官 我們會找到他的\N- Hot tar, Sir. - We'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.32,0:55:03.28,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們接近背部了\NWe're close to black skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.68,0:55:05.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}靠近她\NSneak up on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.94,0:55:16.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}她是我們的了\NShe's ours, Lads.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.20,0:55:50.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那是什麼 勞倫斯先生\NWhat was that, Mr. Lawrence?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.36,0:55:55.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生\NMr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.00,0:56:05.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}媽的\NGod damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.11,0:56:07.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}找勞倫斯過來\NFind Mr. Lawrence...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.00,0:56:52.45,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}找勞倫斯去抽水\NGet Mr. Lawrence to man the pumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.82,0:56:54.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他在哪兒\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.93,0:56:56.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}左舷船頭\NPort bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.40,0:57:10.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}給我最大的魚叉\NGet me the biggest tines we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.03,0:57:15.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他想來一戰\NHe wants a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.51,0:57:28.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我從來沒過鯨這麼做 勞倫斯 掌舵\N- I never seen a whale do that. - Mr. Lawrence, take the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.31,0:57:31.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拉姆斯德爾 把繩子另一頭繫在前桅\NMr. Ramsdell, secure the other end of the line to the foremast.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.57,0:57:32.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}遵命 長官\NAye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.58,0:57:35.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}只要我還活著 他是我的\NAs I live and breathe, he's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.82,0:58:23.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}當心\NLook out!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.93,0:59:17.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長\NCap'n...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.60,0:59:20.91,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號 它在傾斜\NThe Essex, it's listing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.16,0:59:34.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}幫我調頭\NHelp me turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.77,1:00:15.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}勇敢點 在這 過來 尼克森\N- That's it, be brave. - Here! Full ahead, Mr. Nickerson.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.81,1:00:53.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生\NMr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.97,1:00:58.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一頭鯨撞壞了船\NA whale threw her, it stove the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.25,1:01:00.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}什麼\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.38,1:01:02.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們失去了伊斯頓和山本\NWe lost Easton and Sanborn.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.77,1:01:07.45,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}水泵沒用了 長官\NThe pumps are useless, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.31,1:01:17.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}準備棄船 我們不能劃著回去\N- Prepare to abandon ship. - We can't row away home!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.48,1:01:21.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們必須從船上帶走必要的東西\NWe have to strip from the sails and jimmy-rig something.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.16,1:01:21.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}遵命 長官\NAye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.88,1:01:23.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}帶上盡可能多的水和食物\NGet as much food and water as you can carry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.48,1:01:26.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們需要你們能找到的任何一滴水\NWe're gonna need all the fresh water you can find.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.88,1:01:28.97,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們盡可能待在一塊\NWe stick together as much as we can.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.09,1:01:38.58,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查普爾先生 儲備物\NMr. Chappel, the provisions!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.89,1:01:43.36,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}帶上盡可能多的食物\NTake as much food as you can carry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.16,1:01:48.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}清理道路\NMake way!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.71,1:01:52.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拿住 儲備食物\N- Got it? - Hard tack and stock!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.31,1:01:54.89,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}帶上那些蠟燭 船帆下來了\N- Grab the candles there! - Lower away!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.94,1:01:55.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拿上那些儲物櫃\NTake those tack lockers.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.12,1:02:03.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拉上去\NPull her up!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.21,1:02:12.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}快 尼克森\NCome on, Nickerson!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.30,1:02:16.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}當心\NPace yourself!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.42,1:02:44.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}抓住手 我拉到你了 拉他上來\N- Grab the hand! I got you! - Get 'im up!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.73,1:02:58.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}離油遠點\NGotta get away from the oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.38,1:03:03.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}尼克森 查斯先生在哪兒 他剛才還在這 長官\N- Nickerson! Where is Mr. Chase? - He was just here, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.25,1:03:15.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生\NMr. Chase!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.73,1:03:36.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯\NMr. Chase, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.30,1:03:41.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}大副在哪兒 離遠點\N- Where is the first mate? - Away!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.26,1:03:43.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯\NMr. Chase, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.58,1:03:56.89,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯\NMr. Chase, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.03,1:04:47.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他在那兒 他在那兒 他在那兒\NThere he is! There he is! There he is!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.53,1:04:51.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這裏 查斯在那兒\N- Over there! - There's Mr. Chase!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.33,1:04:54.50,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生\NMr. Chase!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.36,1:05:00.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}抓住他了\NWe got him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.99,1:05:09.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們去釣魚是吧\NGoin' fishin', are we?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.46,1:05:11.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}都準備好了 花花公子\NClear and loaded, Mr. Joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.61,1:05:26.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}退後 不然我們會和她一起下沉的\NBack away, or she'll take us down with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.61,1:07:05.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}南美洲以西 2000海里
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.17,1:07:13.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長 我們的食物怎麼辦\NCaptain, what about our provisions?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.21,1:07:22.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}每人每天兩盎司的硬麵餅\NTwo ounces of hardtack a day per man...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.56,1:07:25.40,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}和半杯水\Nand half a cup of water.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.41,1:07:31.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不夠的\NWe can't live on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.59,1:07:51.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是他\NIt's he!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.81,1:07:57.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}對 是他\NYeah, it's him all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.62,1:08:03.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你騙不了我 查斯先生\NYou don't fool me, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.65,1:08:05.73,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}克芬先生 是嗎\N- Mr. Coffin. - That right?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.91,1:08:09.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你帶我們來這的 你知道的\NYou put us here, you know you put us here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.63,1:08:12.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿 放下槍 放下手槍\N- Hey! Put it down. - Put the pistol down!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.91,1:08:13.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}告訴我你害怕了\NSay you're scared!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.11,1:08:15.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}克芬先生 放下槍\NMr. Coffin, put the pistol down!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.74,1:08:16.74,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你清楚食物和水耗盡後會怎樣\NYou know what happens when the food and water runs out!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.39,1:08:20.17,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}按船長說的做 克芬先生\NDo as the Captain says, Coffin!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.22,1:08:20.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我只是想看到\NI just want to see
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.31,1:08:22.97,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}陸人害怕 克芬 放下槍\N- the landsman scared. - Coffin, put the pistol down!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.02,1:08:25.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這是命令 按照船長說的做\N- That's an order! - Do as the Captain says! Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.44,1:08:27.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}說啊 亨利\N- Say it! - Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.06,1:08:29.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}說啊 說啊\NSay it! Say it!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.05,1:08:32.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}亨利 放下槍\NHenry! Put the pistol down.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.50,1:08:40.97,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}亨利 放下槍\NHenry, put it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.30,1:09:19.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後向東\NSo, east it was,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.03,1:09:22.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}按來的路線回去\Nback in the direction we'd come,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.85,1:09:24.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}頂著烈日靠著一個指南針\NWith only the sun and a compass.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.91,1:09:29.16,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}所有的方向都看起來一樣\NAll directions looked the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.88,1:09:33.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們的期望是靠著西風帶漂到復活島\NOur hope was to catch the westerlies to Easter Island,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.12,1:09:36.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}3000英里的距離\Na journey of 3,000 miles.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.58,1:09:39.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}過了12天我們漂到了南方\NFor 12 days we've drifted south.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.33,1:09:42.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}6度緯度\NSix degrees latitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.66,1:09:45.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}離復活島差了十萬八千里\NNot one mile closer to Easter Island.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.91,1:09:52.58,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們被詛咒了\NWe are cursed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.75,1:09:55.71,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}當我們趕上風帶我們會彌補上的\NWe'll make up for it when we catch the variables.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.69,1:10:00.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們會趕上的\NWe'll catch 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.36,1:10:36.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}抓牢了 船長\NHold on, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.24,1:10:44.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}花花公子 帆繩纏住了\NMr. Joy, the halyard's jammed.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.98,1:10:51.36,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}花花公子 抓住它 花花公子\NMr. Joy! Grab at it, Mr. Joy!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.95,1:10:59.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}馬修\NMatthew!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.07,1:11:36.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}馬修 發生了什麼 發生了什麼\NMatthew, okay, what happened? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.44,1:11:39.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你在這幹什麼 讓我看看\N- What are you doing here? - Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.66,1:11:41.79,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 不 不 讓我看看\N- No, no, no. - Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.84,1:11:42.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我沒事 我沒事\NI'm fine, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.90,1:11:45.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}放鬆 我知道 讓我看一眼\NJust relax, I know, I know, let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.25,1:11:53.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我被擊中頭部了 我沒事 好嗎\NI'm hit on the head, it's good, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.86,1:11:56.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}給他些水 我不需要什麼水\N- Give him some water! - I don't need any water!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.17,1:11:58.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}給他他媽的一些水喝\NGive him some God damned water.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.11,1:12:00.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 不 我不需要水 我沒事\NNo, no, no, I don't need water, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.75,1:12:10.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拿著\NTake that, take it!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.84,1:12:13.38,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒事\NI gotcha, I gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.48,1:12:16.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒事的 你會沒事的\NAll right, you'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.97,1:12:22.97,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿 你們在看什麼 我沒事\NHey, what are you all looking at, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.32,1:12:25.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德船長 我裝的\NCap'n Pollard, this is fiddle.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.27,1:12:28.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我忽悠你們的 聽見了嗎\NThis is God damn fiddle, ya hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.41,1:12:30.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}歐文 在\N- Owen. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.59,1:12:33.59,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我沒事 我沒事\NI'm fine, all right, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.98,1:12:37.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我沒事 離開這\N- Thank you. - I'm fine! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.49,1:12:39.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他沒事\NHe is good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.82,1:12:41.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.56,1:12:46.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼在死人身上浪費水\NWhy waste water on a dead man?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.68,1:12:51.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們從小一起航海 情同手足\NFancy men who know each other, sailed together since childhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.87,1:12:53.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你告訴我\NNow, tell me,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.30,1:12:56.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你會坐等著看你的兄弟死去嗎\Ncould you just sit there and watch your own brother die?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.20,1:13:00.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}簡單的算術問題 查普爾先生\NIt's simply a matter of numbers, Mr. Chappel.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.86,1:13:02.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}水不夠我們所有人用\NThere's not enough for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.76,1:13:17.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼在死人身上浪費水\NWhy waste water on a dead man?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.41,1:13:19.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼浪費水\NWhy waste water...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.83,1:13:22.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼浪費水\NWhy waste water?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.01,1:13:25.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼在死人身上浪費水\NWhy waste water on a dead man?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.70,1:13:27.91,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}尼克森先生\NMr. Nickerson?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.30,1:13:31.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼在死人身上浪費水 你還好嗎 先生\N- Why waste water on a dead man? - Are you all right, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.09,1:13:34.59,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不能 不能什麼\N- I cannot. - Cannot what?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.64,1:13:38.84,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 你 你 你知道足夠多了 你瞭解夠多了\NNo, you... you... you have enough, you have more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.89,1:13:40.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是 先生 我們都講到這兒了\NBut, Sir! We've come so far.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.41,1:13:43.71,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們必須善始善終 我們有約定的 先生\N- We have come to an end. - We have an agreement, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.76,1:13:46.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拿著錢離開 這是魔鬼的交易\NTake the money and leave! You've a devil's bargain!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.12,1:13:50.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 長官 魔鬼喜歡隱藏秘密\NNo, Sir, the devil loves his unspoken secrets...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.20,1:13:56.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}特別是那些蠶食人的靈魂的秘密\Nespecially those that fester in a man's soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.81,1:14:00.36,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你的秘密是什麼\NWhat's yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.47,1:14:21.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不是一個好作家\NI'm not a great writer.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.49,1:14:26.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不是霍索恩\NI'm not Hawthorne.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.28,1:14:29.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}從我學寫作以來\NAfter my first hearing of Odysseus,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.14,1:14:32.08,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這個故事一直困擾著我\Nthis tale has haunted me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.87,1:14:35.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}它消耗著我\NIt consumes me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.90,1:14:38.74,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我害怕如果我不寫這個故事\NI fear if I do not write it,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.70,1:14:42.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我會再也沒辦法寫作\NI should never write again.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.93,1:14:45.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}還有什麼\NWhat else?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.10,1:14:49.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我害怕如果我寫這個故事\NI fear if I DO write it,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.63,1:14:53.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}寫出來的不如故事精彩\Nthat it will not be as good as it should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.75,1:15:05.79,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}繼續講這個故事 先生\NContinue the story, Sir...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.71,1:15:08.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為了彼此\Nfor the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.71,1:15:20.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}困住的第34天
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.94,1:15:26.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}傳過去\NPass that down.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.57,1:15:32.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}給\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.26,1:15:41.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們感謝你 主 賜予我們的食物\NWe thank thee, Lord, for this is our food...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.75,1:15:47.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}賜予我們的光 健康 和所有美好的東西\Nfor light, good health, with every good.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.13,1:15:49.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那裏\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.00,1:15:51.03,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}陸地\NLand!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.24,1:15:54.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}陸地 歐文 陸地\NLand, Owen! Land!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.97,1:15:57.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}陸地 陸地 陸地\NLand! Land! Land!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.58,1:16:00.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}划船 快\NRow! Get 'way! Get 'way!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.60,1:16:05.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}划船\NRow!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.35,1:16:27.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}停下 停下 停下\NHold fast! Hold fast! Hold fast!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.68,1:16:30.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯 什麼東西 長官\NMr.Chase, what is it, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.60,1:16:34.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯 那是什麼怪物 你怎麼停下了\NMr. Chase, what the devil is it, why have you stopped?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.26,1:16:36.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他一直在跟著我們 什麼\N- He's been following us. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.38,1:16:39.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那裏什麼都沒有 查斯先生\NThere's nothin' out there, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.80,1:16:41.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那裏什麼都沒有 長官\NThere ain't nothin' out there, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.51,1:16:43.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}長官 你在幹什麼\NSir, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.91,1:17:27.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他在哪兒\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.72,1:19:30.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這可能是迪西島\NIt could be Ducie Island.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.40,1:19:34.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒有地圖 指南針 象限儀 沒辦法確認\NWithout a map, compass or quadrant there's no way to be certain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.75,1:19:36.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們晝夜都亮著火\NWe will keep fires going night and day,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.46,1:19:40.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但願過往的船隻注意到我們的濃煙\Nhope a passing ship catches sight of our smoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.52,1:20:39.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這是我想讓你們看的\NThis is what I wanted you to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.86,1:20:50.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們肯定在這很長時間了\NThey've been here a long time, for no doubt...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.26,1:20:52.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一定也在等船隻\Nwaiting for a ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.96,1:20:55.24,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是沒有船來過\NBut no ship came.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.87,1:20:59.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒有船會來\NNo ship is going to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.63,1:21:02.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果我們呆在這 我們會死\NIf we stay, we die.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.09,1:21:05.24,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你們覺得如果鳥兒過來看到\NHow long do you think it would take to trust the birds
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.31,1:21:07.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}自己的蛋被吃了會多久不再過來\Nto stop coming here once they see their eggs eaten?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.62,1:21:30.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這是知道自己將要死去的好處\NIt's a privilege to know the moment of one's death in advance.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.69,1:21:32.48,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}可以為此準備\NAnd to be able to prepare for it...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.77,1:21:36.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}離家太遠的詛咒\Na curse to be so far from home...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.99,1:21:42.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}或者有機會說再見但沒機會和解\Nor a chance to say goodbyes, without a chance to make peace...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.08,1:21:45.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}或者報仇的機會\Nor a chance to settle scores.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.32,1:21:51.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是 我們之間清楚了\NBut alas, at least those are settled between us,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.49,1:21:52.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長\NCap'n?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.86,1:21:56.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}什麼船長\NCaptain of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.03,1:21:59.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號沉沒了不是你的責任\NThe Essex was lost and no fault o'yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.95,1:22:02.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我該受譴責 你不是船長\N- I was as much to blame... - You were not the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.92,1:22:10.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你天生就是幹這活的料\NYou were born to do this job.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.06,1:22:13.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我只是生下來只能幹這個\NI was just born into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.90,1:22:27.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們幹了什麼 你覺得 喬治\NWhat we do, do ya think, George?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.53,1:22:33.60,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們幹了什麼冒犯了上帝 讓他這麼不開心\NWhat offense did we give God to upset him so?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.65,1:22:36.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}冒犯上帝的是那些白鯨\NThe only creature to have offended God here is the whale.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.35,1:22:38.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不是我們\NNot us?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.45,1:22:44.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不是我們的傲慢 我們的貪婪 看我們現在在哪兒\NNot our arrogance, our greed? Look where we find ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.12,1:22:46.65,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們是上帝按自己喜好創造出來的高級生物\NWe are supreme creatures made in God's own likeness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.05,1:22:49.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們是地球上的主宰\NWe're earthly kings,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.93,1:22:53.73,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們要環航我們居住的星球\Nwhose business it is to circumnavigate the planet bestowed to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.32,1:22:56.48,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}將自然屈服於我們的意志\NAnd to bend nature to OUR will.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.59,1:23:00.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們經歷了這麼多你還覺得主宰一切嗎\NYou really feel like an earthly king after everything that we've been through?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.63,1:23:06.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們什麼都不是 我們是微粒 灰塵 但是我們\N- We're nothing... we're specks... dust. - But we're...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.14,1:23:09.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拂曉時朝太陽方向行駛\NWe sail into the sun at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.56,1:23:14.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果我們要死 死在上帝的光輝裏\NIf we are to die, with God's grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.20,1:23:17.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}讓我們像男人一樣死去\NLet us die as men.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.51,1:23:31.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們準備好了嗎 維克斯先生 是的 長官\N- Are we ready, Mr. Weeks? - Aye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.64,1:23:40.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查普爾先生\NMr. Chappel.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.40,1:23:43.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}萊特先生 我不能 長官\N- Mr. Wright. - I can't do it, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.14,1:23:45.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我 洛克斯 維克斯\NMe, Locks and Weeks...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.18,1:23:48.66,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們留下來\Nwe're stayin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.18,1:23:58.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}準備出發 馬修\NReady to go, Matthew?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.67,1:24:12.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我來幫你一把 有什麼用\N- I'll give you a hand here... - What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.54,1:24:14.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你聽見我說的嗎 不 我們一起回家 一起回家\N- You hear me? - No, we're goin' home, we're goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.77,1:24:16.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒用的\NThere's no point.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.96,1:24:18.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}走吧\NJust go.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.22,1:24:24.44,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}媽的 馬修\NGod damn it, Matthew.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.14,1:24:28.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒事的\NIt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.51,1:24:31.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我回家立馬派一艘船過來接你\NI'll send a boat for you the minute we get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.82,1:24:34.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後我們回到楠塔基特玩牌 好嗎\NAnd we'll play cards back in Nantucket, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.75,1:24:37.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}好 一言為定 好\N- Yeah, it's a deal. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.51,1:24:46.43,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你要我幫你打開水壺嗎\NYou want me to open that for ya?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.43,1:24:52.58,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我能行的\NNaw, I think I'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.74,1:25:00.40,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}上帝保佑你 兄弟\NGod be with you, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.21,1:25:04.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}也保佑你\NAnd you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.58,1:25:24.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}彼得森\NBrother Peterson?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.93,1:25:28.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你一起跟我們走吧 彼得森先生\N- Y'all comin' with us? - Mr. Peterson.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.06,1:25:31.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}和邦德一起登船走吧\NWhy don't you come on our boat with Mr. Bond.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.06,1:26:02.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}困住的第48天
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.63,1:26:07.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}在哪兒 他在哪兒\NWhere... where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.22,1:26:09.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德\NPollard.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.74,1:26:13.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}勞倫斯先生 勞倫斯先生 醒醒\NMr. Lawrence, Mr. Lawrence, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.84,1:26:16.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}另一條船去哪兒了\NWhere has the other boat gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.33,1:26:19.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德 波拉德 船長波拉德\N- Pollard! Pollard! - Captain Pollard!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.57,1:26:22.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德 波拉德 船長波拉德\N- Pollard! Pollard! - Cap'n Pollard!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.48,1:26:24.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德 船長\N- Pollard! - Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.63,1:26:31.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德\NPollard!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.43,1:26:36.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}休息會兒\NGet some rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.64,1:26:54.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}本傑明 你在幹什麼\NBenjamin, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.90,1:26:56.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他死了\NHe's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.01,1:26:58.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}把他丟海裏 長官\NThrowing him overboard, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.54,1:27:03.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}看著我 看著我 本傑明\NLook at me, look at me Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.34,1:27:12.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒有理智的水手會丟棄也許會救自己一命的東西\NNo right minded sailor discards what might yet save him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.35,1:27:25.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}聽我說 孩子 聽我說\NListen to me, Boy, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.72,1:27:31.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他能救我們\NHe can help us.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.97,1:27:34.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我的上帝 我們神聖的\NMy God, our heavenly...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.25,1:27:42.79,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這些生物每日祈盼著食物\NThy creatures wait On Thee for daily food.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.03,1:28:02.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}決定了\NSo it was decided.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.00,1:28:11.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們準備了屍體\NWe prepared the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.06,1:28:16.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們去除了內臟\NWe removed the organs.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.78,1:28:21.28,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}分割了他的四肢\NSeparated his limbs from his body.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.88,1:28:25.91,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}從骨頭上切下了所有的肉\NAnd cut all the flesh from the bones.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.97,1:28:31.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後\NAfter which...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.34,1:28:34.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們拼起了屍塊\Nwe closed body.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.72,1:28:37.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後把屍體縫起來\NAnd then we sewed it up...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.62,1:28:39.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}盡我們所能\Nas decently as we could...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.14,1:28:42.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後扔到了海裏\Nand committed it to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.51,1:28:46.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們先吃了心臟\NWe ate the heart first.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.01,1:28:56.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你有意見\NYou judge me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.62,1:29:00.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.29,1:29:09.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個\NThere... there...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.77,1:29:11.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}說完了\Nit's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.29,1:29:16.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}說完了\NIt is out.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.47,1:29:19.24,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你從未告訴過任何人\NYou never told anyone?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.04,1:29:23.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.76,1:29:26.59,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}包括你的妻子\NNot even your wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.39,1:29:29.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你覺得如果她知道我做的罪孽\NDo you think she could ever love me,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.03,1:29:32.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}她還會愛我嗎\Nif she knew the abominations I had committed?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.98,1:29:35.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 她還會愛你的\NYes, she would.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.54,1:29:39.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果你和我相遇的時候告訴我\NAnd if you had told me this story when we met,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.57,1:29:43.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我今天還會是你的妻子\NI would still wear your ring today.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.12,1:29:47.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個男孩的勇敢\NThe strength of that boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.29,1:29:49.58,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}還在你內心\Nstill lives in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.58,1:29:53.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我看得出\NI see that...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.07,1:29:55.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}即使你自己不覺察\Neven if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.15,1:30:19.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你可以說完你的故事了 親愛的\NYou can finish your story now, My Love.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.85,1:30:32.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿\NLook...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.63,1:30:37.70,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}坐起來\NSit up.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.30,1:30:41.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}聽著\NListen.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.71,1:30:44.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}媽的\NDamn thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.15,1:30:49.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們還有些水\NWe still got a few drops of the water left.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.76,1:30:52.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}別放棄 我們要回家了\NDon't ya quit on me, we're goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.01,1:30:59.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你還有家人在嗎\NDo you have a family...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.46,1:31:02.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生\Nback home, Mr. Chase?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.33,1:31:03.71,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}有的 我的妻子\NYeah, I have wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.56,1:31:10.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}對 還有一個兒子和一個女兒\NYes, and a son or a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.56,1:31:27.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}困住的第71天 南美以西1200海里
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.07,1:31:57.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}好\NVery well.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.39,1:32:00.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長 我們重新抽籤\NCap'n, we'll draw again.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.36,1:32:02.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們不會這麼做\NWe'll do no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.60,1:32:06.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們重新抽 拉姆斯德爾先生\N- We'll draw again. - Mr. Ramsdell,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.36,1:32:10.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你要用這槍來指揮\Nyou will assume command of this vessel.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.03,1:32:16.17,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你明白\NYa got that?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.22,1:32:19.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你是我們的船長 你的船員需要你\NYou're our cap'n, your men need you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.61,1:32:22.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船員沒事的\NThe men will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.18,1:32:26.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拜託了 拜託了\NPlease. Please. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.99,1:32:28.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}亨利 讓我們再抽籤\N- Henry... - Let us go again.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.59,1:32:31.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這是命令\NIt is an order.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.63,1:32:34.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果你做不到\NIf you cannot do it,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.63,1:32:36.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}把槍給其他人\Npass the pistol to another man.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.96,1:33:24.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們在赤道無風帶幾周了\NWe were weeks in the Doldrums.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.39,1:33:27.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}太平洋那片區域遠比海洋枯竭\NThat part of the Pacific is more desert than ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.87,1:33:30.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}太陽炙熱\NThe sun beating down...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.81,1:33:32.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我害怕\NMy fear...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.27,1:33:35.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我能想到的是\NAll I could think about...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.76,1:33:40.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}所有人都會死而我是最後一個活著的\Nwas that everyone would die and I'd be the last left alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.75,1:33:46.34,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯只知道我們離陸地還有800英里\NWell, as best as Mr. Chase could tell, we were still 800 miles from land.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.01,1:33:53.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生\NMr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.51,1:34:03.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長波拉德\NCap'n Pollard.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.58,1:34:07.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}很高興見到你\NVery happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.11,1:34:10.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們生存下來沒什麼值得高興\NVery little happiness in our survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.30,1:34:15.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們也是 長官\NNor in ours, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.44,1:34:17.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}巴爾齊萊號\NBarzillai?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.68,1:34:21.03,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}另一艘船\NThe third boat?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.28,1:34:26.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們不見了 幾天不見了\NThey're gone, they've been gone for days.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.99,1:34:29.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我估計他們迷失了 長官\NI'm afraid they're lost, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.07,1:35:01.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生 你為這個準備好了\NMr. Chase, you are prepared for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.97,1:35:19.95,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不過是頭白鯨\NIt's just a whale.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.71,1:35:25.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那裏 投茅\NThere! Throw the lance!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.63,1:35:27.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}投啊\NThrow it!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.70,1:35:34.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}投啊\NThrow it, drown the lad!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.64,1:35:48.32,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}投啊\NThrow it!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.16,1:36:01.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}就是現在 投茅啊\NDo it! Now! Throw the lance!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.51,1:36:22.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你為什麼不投\NWhy didn't you throw it?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.12,1:36:49.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你他媽是個傻子\NYou're a damn fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.04,1:37:15.91,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}洋流把我們拆散了\NThe current drew us apart...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.80,1:37:20.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那是我們最後一次見到船長波拉德的鯨船\Nand that was the last we would see of Captain Pollard's whale boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.80,1:37:23.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}困住的第87天
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.11,1:37:25.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一艘船\NA boat!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.54,1:37:27.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}前方有一艘船\NA boat on the forward bow!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.16,1:37:55.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}上帝仁慈\NMay god have mercy.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.16,1:38:11.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}困住的第90天 1821年2月18日
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.64,1:38:39.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生\NMr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.35,1:38:44.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}父親\NFather...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.06,1:38:48.50,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}別丟下我 父親\Ndon't leave me, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.26,1:39:40.40,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿 長官\NHey, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.04,1:39:45.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生 長官 看 看 長官\NMr. Chase. Sir. Look. Look, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.01,1:39:50.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}長官\NSir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.86,1:39:53.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}看 那裏\NLook. Out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.45,1:39:54.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們來了\NThey're coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.81,1:40:01.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們來救我們了\NThey're coming for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.10,1:40:28.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們在那裏被救了\NWe were rescued there, off the Isle of Mбs Afuera, Chile,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.99,1:40:32.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號沉船90天後\Nninety days after the sinking of the Essex.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.40,1:40:37.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們給我們一些衣服和皮革吃\NThey gave us some old clothes... leathers, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.38,1:40:42.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}起先感覺很難吃\NIt was hard to eat at first... strange.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.41,1:40:45.20,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們盡力照顧我們\NThey looked after us as best they could,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.30,1:40:48.50,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後他們找到了可以帶我們回家的一艘船\Nthen we found a ship that could carry us home.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.34,1:40:52.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}回家又花了三個月\NThat voyage took another three months.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.34,1:40:55.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}1821年6月11日 楠塔基特港口
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.70,1:41:04.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}全島的人好像都過來看我們回來\NIt looked like the whole Island turned out to see us return.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.40,1:41:09.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是沒有歡呼 只有沉寂\NBut there were no cheers... only silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.27,1:41:17.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們看我們的樣子像是看到鬼 幽靈\NThey looked at us like we were... apparitions... phantoms.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.81,1:41:22.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們沒有對任何人說起我們生存的細節\NWe'd said nothing of the details of our survival to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.13,1:41:26.17,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是我猜他們知道我們的困境\NBut I wondered if they somehow knew of our privations.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.32,1:41:29.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}也許他們只是好奇\NMaybe they were just curious.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.14,1:42:19.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我保證過的 不是嗎\NI promised, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.58,1:42:28.71,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}天啊\NGod.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.96,1:42:34.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿 寶貝 你是誰啊\NHey, Sweetie! Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.15,1:42:37.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}菲比安\NPhebe Ann.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.10,1:42:42.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}菲比安·查斯\NPhebe Ann Chase.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.00,1:42:45.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他是你的父親\NIt's your Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.42,1:42:49.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿 寶貝\NHey, Sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.00,1:42:56.43,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他是你的父親\NIt's your Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.27,1:43:15.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}當然還是有人找上他\NOf course they couldn't leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.78,1:43:18.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生和他的妻子往家走了不久\NMr. Chase and his wife had scarcely walked a block towards home
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.80,1:43:21.95,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他就被攔下來並帶回了海事辦公室\Nwhen he was stopped and made to return to the Maritime Office.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.41,1:43:26.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}生意上的事還有疑問\NThere were business matters still in question.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.12,1:43:41.78,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}對於這件事\NSo, to the matter...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.18,1:43:49.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}因為我們此次航線造成了巨大的人員和財產損失\NDue to the significant loss of life and property on our voyage,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.19,1:43:52.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}將會有一場聽證會\Nit seems there will be an inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.14,1:43:57.58,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}作為船長和大副 我們需要交待事實經過\NAnd, as Captain and first mate, we will be expected to give account of what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.03,1:43:59.36,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是的 當然\NYes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.42,1:44:04.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我就這件事和船主和我父親討論過\NAnd, having discussed this with the ship owners and... my father,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.11,1:44:08.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}顯然完全交待經過會有後果\Nit is clear that full disclosure will have ramifications...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.34,1:44:12.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}對整個行業有可怕的後果\Nterrible ramifications for whole industry.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.13,1:44:15.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一頭白鯨弄沉了埃塞克斯號\NThat a whale brought down the Essex.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.66,1:44:18.95,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但這是事實\NBut it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.11,1:44:30.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果保險商和投資人開始擔心\NIf the insurance houses and investors were to start worrying about...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.08,1:44:32.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}海怪把船弄沉\Nsea monsters sinking ships,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.30,1:44:36.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}水手們很難活下來\Nsailors drawing lots to survive...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.27,1:44:40.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們在石油行業 所有人\NWe are in the oil business... all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.50,1:44:47.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}在任何一個行業成功的機率一定要比失敗的風險要高\NAnd as in any business the probability of success must always be greater the risk incurred.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.79,1:44:50.66,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那麼 你有什麼建議 喬治\NSo, what are you suggesting, George?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.89,1:44:53.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你就說船擱淺了\NThat you say that the ship ran aground.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.27,1:44:56.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那是個謊言 並且說船員是淹死的\N- That's a lie. - And that the men that died drowned.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.41,1:44:58.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那也是個謊言\NThat's another lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.24,1:45:00.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}想想吧 他們會讓你當船長\NThink on it... they will make you captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.23,1:45:02.50,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個我是有書面保證的\NOh! That pledge I already have in writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.61,1:45:06.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個前提是你帶回一船的鯨油\NOnly on the condition you bring home a ship full of oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.87,1:45:09.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這麼做會確保你這件事\NThis way it's guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.75,1:45:12.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你會變成有錢人\NYou would be a wealthy man.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.18,1:45:16.48,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯不再是陸人的名字 而是有記錄的\NThe name Chase need no longer be a landsman's name, but an established name
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.51,1:45:20.03,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}屬於楠塔基特島偉大家族的名字\Nthat belongs among the great families of Nantucket.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.81,1:45:23.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你要我為了功名掩蓋發生的一切\NYou want me to whitewash what happened for profit?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.07,1:45:27.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們是要你務實些\NWe're asking you to be pragmatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.75,1:45:45.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號是被一頭白鯨撞沉的\NThe Essex was stoved by a white whale.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.04,1:45:48.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們倖存下來的在裝備不良的捕鯨船上\NAnd those of us that survived in ill-equipped whale boats
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.94,1:45:53.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}只能靠犯下罪孽才能存活\Nhad to commit abominations in order to survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.27,1:45:57.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們回來後 又被指望傳播公然露骨的謊言\NAnd on our return, we're expected to spread barefaced lies,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.77,1:46:00.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}好讓你們這些楠塔基特島島船主們\Nso that you, the ship owners of Nantucket,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.38,1:46:04.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}賺錢晚上再睡得安穩覺嗎\Nmight line your pockets and sleep well at night?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.41,1:46:08.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不會掩蓋真相\NWell, I will not embroil the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.93,1:46:10.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}喬治 你也不應該\NNor should you, George.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.27,1:46:32.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我最後一次見他\NThat last time I saw him...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.47,1:46:33.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生 長官\NMr. Chase, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.32,1:46:37.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我說不出我想說的話\NI couldn't find the right words to say what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.74,1:46:40.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}湯姆斯\NThomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.01,1:46:42.78,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}也許我沒什麼想說的\NPerhaps there ARE no words.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.18,1:46:48.20,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我 我要去法爾茅斯了\NI'm... I'm gonna be on my way to Falmouth, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.33,1:46:52.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個\Nit's...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.12,1:46:55.43,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個 很榮幸 長官\Nit's... it's been an honor, Sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.75,1:46:57.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}能夠服務於您\Nto serve with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.83,1:47:03.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是我的榮幸 尼克森先生\NThe honor has been mine, Mr. Nickerson.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.82,1:47:22.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拿著\NTake it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.10,1:47:29.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}祝你好運 湯姆斯\NGood luck out there, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.11,1:47:31.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}謝謝 長官\NThank you, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.70,1:48:03.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}第二天喬治·波拉德被召喚到聽證會\NNext day George Pollard was called before the inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.53,1:48:10.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}先生們 船長喬治·波拉德\NGentlemen, Captain George Pollard.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.41,1:48:13.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}楠塔基特所有重要人物都在那兒\NAll the important men of Nantucket were there...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.96,1:48:17.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這是慣例\Nit was a formality.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.91,1:48:20.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}日安 船長 請坐\NGood day to you, Captain, please sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.88,1:48:27.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}事實是\NFor the record then.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.51,1:48:35.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號是在厄瓜多爾以西被一頭1200多米長的白鯨撞沉的\NThe Essex was stoved by a white whale 12 hundred meters west of Ecuador.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.20,1:48:38.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}就像歐文·查斯說的那樣\NIt was as if Owen Chase himself had spoken.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.90,1:48:42.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他告訴了他們真相\NHe told them the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.37,1:48:47.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長波拉德的良心發現了\NCap'n Pollard's conscience was clear...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.07,1:48:51.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但那場聽證會是個恥辱\Nbut the inquiry was a sham.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.02,1:48:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.51,1:49:01.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}至於那頭白鯨 他們再也沒有找到\Nover the white whale... they never found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.78,1:49:05.71,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他再一次出航但在夏威夷擱淺\NHe ran a second ship aground off of Hawaii...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.82,1:49:08.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}兩次詛咒\Ntwice cursed.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.63,1:49:11.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}再也沒有出航過\NNever sailed again.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.56,1:49:13.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}歐文·查斯\NAnd Owen Chase?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.31,1:49:16.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他說到做到\NHe was a man of his word.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.78,1:49:19.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他派了一艘船去了杜斯特島\NFirst, he sent a boat back to Ducie Island.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.82,1:49:22.66,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}花花公子已經死了\NMr. Joy had passed...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.92,1:49:26.43,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是其他人居然還都活著\Nbut the other three were incredibly still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.28,1:49:30.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後呢\NAnd then?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.07,1:49:34.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他帶著家人搬到了新貝德福德\NThen he packed up his family and moved to New Bedford...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.66,1:49:38.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}去重新開始生活\Nto start over...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.77,1:49:40.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}在一家商店\Nin a merchant...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.07,1:49:43.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}完成自己的人生旅程\Nsailing his own terms.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.68,1:49:56.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你用錢換到故事了 梅爾維爾先生\NWell, you certainly got your money's worth, Mr. Melville.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.40,1:49:58.79,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這二月的夜晚真是一年中最漫長的\NThese February nights are the longest of the year.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.08,1:50:02.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你們都可以休息了 我不行\N- Well, you can both rest now. - Leave me...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.45,1:50:05.32,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我還有一段時間不能休息\NI shall not be resting for some time.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.57,1:50:07.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.72,1:50:12.89,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你得到了你的故事 情節都有了\NYa got your story there, and your plot is all there.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.94,1:50:16.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}也許我想要的不是情節\NMaybe it wasn't a plot I was after.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.82,1:50:18.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不是 那是什麼\NNo, what then?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.06,1:50:21.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你今晚給我的其他東西\NSomething else you've given me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.61,1:50:23.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是什麼\NWhat is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.70,1:50:28.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}敢於去別人不敢去的地方的勇氣\NThe courage to go where... one does not want to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.81,1:50:31.65,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}梅爾維爾先生\NMr. Melville,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.94,1:50:34.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你聽到的 我告訴你的\Nwhat you've heard, what I've told you,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.67,1:50:42.16,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是否都會成為你書中的一部分\Nwill it all be of service to your book?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.25,1:50:46.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這會是部虛構的小說 尼克森先生\NIt will be a work of fiction, Mr. Nickerson,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.00,1:50:49.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}受真實事件啟發\Ninspired by truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.04,1:50:54.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但我不覺得我會用全部事實\Nbut I don't believe I'll feel the need to use all of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.40,1:51:04.73,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}謝謝 給\N- Thank you. - Here...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.21,1:51:06.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拿著這個\Ntake that with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.48,1:51:08.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 錢是給你的 我堅持\NNo, the money is for you, I insist.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.99,1:51:11.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我堅持你要收下\NI insist you keep it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.57,1:51:16.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我堅持這談話裏還是有一個人是清醒的\NAnd I insist that one person in this conversation is sober.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.27,1:51:29.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}該回馬薩諸塞州皮茨菲爾德了\NSo, it's back to Pittsfield, Massachusetts.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.82,1:51:32.38,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}祝你好運\NWell, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.49,1:51:34.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.19,1:51:39.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你知道嗎\NYa know...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.95,1:51:43.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我聽說賓夕法尼亞州一個人最近在地上鑽了一個洞\NI heard a man from Pennsylvania drilled a hole in the ground recently,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.60,1:51:46.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}發現了油\Nand found oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.80,1:51:48.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不會是真的吧\NThat can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.12,1:51:50.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我也聽說過\NI heard it, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.44,1:51:55.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}地上的油\NOil from ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.57,1:51:59.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}真想不到\NFancy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.57,1:52:38.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}赫爾曼·梅爾維爾 1850年完成了他的小說
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.57,1:52:48.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一年後白鯨記發表
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.57,1:52:58.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,280)\fscx50\fscy100}對於白鯨記納撒尼爾·霍桑盛讚它會成為美國偉大的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:07.20,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}翻譯：閒著沒事幹的MT 隨便改
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:18.89,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}人類如何瞭解未知\NHow does one come to know The Unknowable?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:21.70,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}人類需要什麼技能\NWhat faculties must a man possess?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:23.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}自從人類發現鯨油\NSince it was discovered that whale oil
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:27.16,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}可以以前所未有的方式點亮我們的城市\Ncould light our cities in ways never achieved before,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:29.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}全世界需求量暴漲\Nit created global demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:33.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}使人類向開始向\NIt had pushed man to venture further and further
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:36.08,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}海洋更深處冒險\Ninto The Deep, Blue Unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:38.59,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們不知道海洋的深度\NWe know not its depths,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:41.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}也不瞭解海洋裏的生物\Nnor the host of creatures that live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:45.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}怪物是否真的存在\NMonsters, are they real?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:02:00.08,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}或者這些故事只是讓我們對海洋隱藏的秘密有所敬畏\NOr do the stories exist only to make us respect the sea's dark secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:11.08,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}楠塔基特島 馬薩諸塞州 1850年二月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這個問題使我即苦惱又興奮\NThe question both vexes and excites me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:19.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}也是我再次向您寫信請求一次會面的原因\Nand is the reason I've written you a second time to request a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.09,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一次和您交談的機會 先生\NA conversation with you, Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:24.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我相信這會對我將要寫的小說有很大幫助\NI believe will serve me well for the novel I intend to write,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:27.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}小說暫且名為 白鯨記\Ncurrently entitled Moby Dick
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:30.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我期望您能考慮我的提議\NI hope you will reconsider my offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:37.78,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}未知 我的想像力始終想冒險的地方\NThe Unknown, that is where my imagination yearns to venture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.20,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}始終折磨我的問題是\NAnd so, the question plagues me still:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:44.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}人類如何才能探索未知\NHow does a man come to know The Unknowable?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}此致 赫爾曼·梅爾維爾\NSincerely, Herman Melville.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:51.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們打烊了\NWe're closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:53.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}8點後不接客\NNo borders after eight o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:06.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你居然來了\NYou came.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}親愛的 有人來看你\NThere's someone here for you, My Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}湯姆·尼克森\NTom Nickerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}赫爾曼·梅爾維爾\NHerman Melville.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:25.84,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們收到了你的來信\NWe received your letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:30.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你要麼走投無路要麼是個傻子大老遠跑來楠塔基特\NYou're either a desperate man or a fool to come all the way to Nantucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:36.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我的提議還在\NWell, my offer still stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:39.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}3個月的住宿換一晚的交談\NThree months'lodgings for a single night's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:42.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這是我所有的錢了\NIt's all I have in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:45.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但我更願意看作是一次投資\NBut I'd prefer to think of it as an investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:48.71,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我想要你告訴我\NI want you to tell me what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號發生了什麼\Nto the Essex.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:59.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你覺得發生了什麼\NWell,what do you think happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:02.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}有傳言埃塞克斯號\NThere are rumblings,rumors that the Essex...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:05.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你想要什麼 期望聽到什麼故事\NWhat do you want?What story do you expect to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:08.03,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}白鯨的故事\NThat of The Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:14.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號擱淺了 有完整的報告\NThe Essex ran aground, there was a full inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我覺得那份報告不是事實全部\NI believe the inquiry was less than truthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:19.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}滾出去\NGet out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}先生 你是埃塞克斯號上唯一的倖存者\NYou are the last survivor or the Essex, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果你不說出來 誰還能講出事實\NIf you won't talk, who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:30.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你沒聽見我的話嗎 出去\NYou do not hear me, leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:37.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你不能走 拜託 就一會兒  他沒心情談\N- You mustn't go, please, just take a minute... - He's in no mind to talk, and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不是大老遠來就是為了被羞辱和浪費時間\NI haven't come all this way to be humiliated and waste my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:41.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拜託了 梅爾維爾 先生\NPlease, Mr. Melville,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:48.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他從來不跟別人談論埃塞克斯號 包括我 從不\Nhe won't talk about the Essex to me, to anyone... never has... never.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.97,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我一點都不瞭解他\NI don't know anything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:58.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他的精神在受折磨 需要救贖\NHis soul is... in torment, and in need of confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拜託了 請讓我和他談 拜託了\NPlease, just let me talk to him... please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:10.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}親愛的\NLove,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:17.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我覺得和這個年輕人談會對你有好處\NI believe it would do you good to talk to the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:19.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:25.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你聽著\NYou listen well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:29.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你酗酒要死的時候誰撐著這個家了\NWho holds this place together while you drink yourself to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:33.20,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你必須和這個年輕人談\NYou WILL talk with this man, as much as is necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:35.44,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}才能保住你的錢\Nto keep the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你知道我們的處境 湯姆\NYou know our circumstances, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:53.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我只說必要的\NOnly as much as is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我去拿威士忌\NI'll get whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:09.84,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我忘了在信裏提到我曾經是一名捕鯨手\NI neglected to mention it in my letter, but I was a whaler once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:14.91,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}有過一次出航 新手\NOne trip. I mean... green hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:17.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那麼你應該都經歷過了\NSo, you've seen it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:21.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我妻子讀過你的書\NMy wife read your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:26.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}她很喜歡 很高興聽到\N- She enjoyed them. - Happy to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}銷量很好 但我估計這個故事\NThey had good sales, but I think that THIS story
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:34.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}甚至能超過我銷量不錯的第一部小說\Ncould surpass even the success of my first novel... which did quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:38.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}又一個你的航海軼事\NAnother of your seafaring yarns.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:44.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你聽說過霍索恩嗎 梅爾維爾先生\NHave you read Hawthorne, Mr. Melville?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:50.03,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}當下有一名作家 一個大作家\NNow, there's a writer, a great writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:51.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他是的\NHe is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:57.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但他不在這兒 因為我自己的原因\NBut he is not here, and I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:00.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我在這兒\Nfor my own particular reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:12.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我會告訴你埃塞克斯號 我相信你會失望的\NI'll tell you of the Essex, I believe you will be disappointed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:15.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但我說的每個字都是真實的\Nbut every word I say will be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:21.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號的故事就是兩個男人的故事\NThe story of the Essex is the story of two men...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:24.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}喬治·波拉德船長\NCaptain George Pollard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:29.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}和他大副 歐文·查斯\Nand his first mate, Owen Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:33.09,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}歐文 你不能遲到\NOwen, you don't want to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:38.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我會到那兒的 再說了 不能讓我們的女兒睡在破陋的房子裏對吧\NI'll be there, besides, can't have our daughter sleeping under a leaky roof, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.71,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你為什麼那麼肯定是女兒\NWhat makes you so sure it's a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:45.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}肯定是的 她會提醒我你這麼固執為什麼我還是愛你\NWell, it has to be, so she can remind me why I have to love you, and you being stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果是女兒她會更像你而不是我\NIf it's to to be a daughter she'll be a version of you, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:51.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}金髮而且一心想征服世界\NBlond locks and determined to conquer the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:55.16,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我想過了今天你會用那件外套換一套制服\NI suppose after today you'll be tradin' in that tunic for a uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:08:00.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒錯 終於能離開這破地方去賺個區艾瑟 船長該住的房子了\NThat's right, finally out of this patch of dirt for a captain's house in Quaise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.79,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不想住在周邊都是古板的鄰居的房子裏\NI don't need one of those houses in town with stuffy neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這裏有足夠供我們一家三口居住的地方\NThere's plenty room here for the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:10.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}有時候你的溫情真讓人受不了\NYa know, sometimes your kind heart and good nature is just unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:14.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}去做你的船長吧\NGo get your captaincy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}- 你下注 1美元9分\N- What's your bid? - One ninety.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.40,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我用2美元買到了一千加侖\NI've got a thousand gallons at two dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我佔40份\NI'll take 40 shares.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:08.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}賣家 賣家 在這\NSeller, seller, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:16.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}克雷斯拉回來了1600桶\NCriterion's back with a fine haul, 1600 barrels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:21.17,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}倫敦市場新紀錄 50磅銀器換燈芯\NA new record, 50 pounds Sterling for headmatter on the London market.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:33.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}早上好 查斯先生\NGood morning Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}馬森先生 請進\N- Mr. Mason. - Come in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:40.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我的合夥人 本傑明·福勒\NMy partner, Benjamin Fuller.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}早上好 先生 請坐\N- Good morning, Sir. - Do sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:51.34,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生 我們希望你知道我們對你\NMr. Chase, I do hope you realize how satisfied we are
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為我們多年的工作有多麼滿意\Nwith the work you've done for us over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}謝謝 先生\NOh, thank you, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們其中一艘船 埃塞克斯號\NAnd one of our ships, the Essex
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:02.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}已經花大價錢修整好準備出海了\Nhas just be refitted at great expense and is to go to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:04.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}因為在她身上花了大價錢\NNow, having made such an investment in her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:08.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們希望確保她在最適合的人手裏\Nwe want to be sure she's in the best possible hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}所以\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:14.20,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們很高興邀請你成為這艘船的\Nit gives us great pleasure to offer you a position aboard her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:16.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}大副\Nas first mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:21.79,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}大副 是的\N- As first mate? - Uh-hum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:26.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}馬森先生 你許諾過我上次出航帶回來1500桶的話\NMr. Mason, you... you promised me command of a ship after my last voyage when
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:30.89,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}會讓我當一艘船的船長 你保證過的\NI brought you back 1500 barrels, do you remember? You gave me your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:33.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個承諾要推遲了\NThat promise must now be deferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:37.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}像別人一樣我們最近行情不好\NLike everyone else we've had a mean time recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.66,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我看不是\NWell, never on my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:43.60,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}楠塔基特主宰了全球市場 這點不能變\NNantucket now dominates the world market, that must not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:46.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒有時間來試驗\NThis is no time for experimentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:50.40,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號必須由喬治·波拉德指揮\NThe Essex will be captained by George Pollard,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:53.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}偉大的捕鯨家族的後裔\Nscion of a great whaling family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:57.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他的父親也是我們的老主顧\NHis father also happens to be our patron.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:01.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}血統 查斯先生 你可以有出色的航海技能\NBlood, Mr. Chase, you can have all the voyages under your belt you want
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:03.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但血統還是更重要\Nbut blood will always win out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.73,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是血統不會幫你的船裝滿油回來 馬森先生\NYes, well, blood's not gonna fill the ship with oil, Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:10.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}要成功指揮船 船長需要被人尊重 如果別人不尊重他怎麼辦\NTo successfully command, a captain needs respect, now, what if the men don't respect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:13.28,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你就要確保別人尊重他\NYou will make sure that they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}再見 先生們\NGood day, Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:17.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我理解你的失落\NI understand your disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:18.95,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}所以\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:22.09,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}115金幣\NA one-fifteenth lay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:26.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我從來沒有給新長官支付過這麼多\NAnd that's more than I've ever paid any first officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:31.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果你帶回來2000桶油 我向你保證\NAnd if you bring back 2000 barrels of oil, I'll give you my word,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}下次你就會是船長\Nnext time you WILL have your captaincy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.45,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你之前給過我保證來 馬森先生\NYou've given me your word before, Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:43.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這次我需要書面保證\NSo, this time I'll take it in writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:12:01.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德船長 我們和查斯先生達成了協議\NCaptain Pollard, we've just had a most agreeable conversation with Mr. Chase,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他會很榮幸服務於您\Nwho'd be honored to serve under you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:07.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我很高興聽到\NI'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}現在我得照顧個沒經驗的\NNow I'm to babysit a greenhorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:14.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一個含著他媽的金勺長大的船長了\NSome cheerless Nantucket born with a damned silver spoon in his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.08,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我真應該當面拒絕\NI should have thrown their offer back in their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:20.05,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼 你已經拿到書面承諾了\NWhy? You now have the offer of command in writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:23.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}騙子的世界什麼都是假的 即使是書面承諾\NYes, well, a liar's word is worthless, even ON paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:36.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你知道即使你是商人我還是會愛上你的\NYou know I'd love you just as much if you were a merchant captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你不能離開兩年之久\NAnd you wouldn't be gone for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.44,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不會離開兩年之久的\NI won't be gone two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}貝德福德家的捕鯨人上周回來了 離開了有三年\NA Bedford whaler came back last week was gone three.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}她失去了兩個男人 而且驚魂落魄\NShe lost two men and still with her hull half empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:49.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們是貝德福德家 沒有我在\NWell, they were from Bedford and they didn't have me aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}婊子養的\NSon of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:01.28,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我要指揮我自己的船\NI will captain my own ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:03.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一艘捕鯨船\Na whaling ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:07.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}靠他們我們只能永遠在這個鬼地方\NUp to them all we'd ever have is a patch of dirt
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不會讓這發生的 佩吉\Nand that's not going to happen, Peggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你父親也是這麼說的 你不能這麼說\NThose'd be your father's words, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:12.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他的話怎麼了\NWhat's wrong with his words?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.34,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他想要為家人為自己爭取\NHe wanted things for his family, for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:19.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他是個夢想家 歐文 是的 他是\N- He was a dreamer, Owen - Yes, he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:23.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}夢想大海 不帶那些廢物們出海\NDreamed of the sea and never got to sea with men like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}至少他看到了他的孩子出生\NAt least he got to see his children born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我只能幹這些\NIt's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}對不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.97,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我嫁給了一個捕鯨人\NI married a whaleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:59.34,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我會盡快回來 我發誓\NI'll come back as quick as the sun is night, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:13.73,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一定要回來 向我保證\NPlease come back... promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我已經向你發誓了 你還要我保證\NI already swore to you, now you want me to promise, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我保證\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}孩子 跟你說句話\NSon, a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:47.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}當船長 你不能當他們的朋友 你是他們的長官\NTo be a captain, you cannot be a friend, you are their superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:51.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}別忘了這點 讓別人記住這點\NNever forget that, never let THEM forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}謝謝\NThank you, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:57.45,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你的曾祖父和其他人創立了這個行業\NYour great-grandfather and a few others created this industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:15:02.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒有我們 沒有你們 世界將會陷入黑暗\NWithout us, without you, the world plunges into darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:05.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我希望能讓家族名譽生輝 先生\NI hope to bring honor to the Pollard family name, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:18.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}啊 上帝創造了巨大的鯨 體長無比的神奇怪物\NThou didst, O Lord, create the mighty whale, That wondrous monster of a mighty length;
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:22.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}頭碩身龐尾又闊 無邊雄力人難度\NBeyond conception his unmeasured strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:28.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}恆古上帝宥永生 吾儕荏弱落凡塵\NBut, everlasting God, thou dost ordain that we, poor feeble mortals
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:33.50,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}妻兒一家須偷生\Nshould engage ourselves, our wives and children to maintain,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:38.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}賴此巨物維生存\NThis dreadful monster with a martial rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:46.36,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}啊 上帝 用您的榮耀之光照亮這些男人\NO Father, grant that your glorious light shine on these men,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:49.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}保佑他們豐收的航程\Nand assure them a prosperous voyage,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:53.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}保佑他們安全歸來\Nthat they may return SAFELY unto the womb ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:57.03,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}楠塔基特的白鯨油\NSo that the white whales of Nantucket whale oil
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:16:00.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}可以繼續照亮我們的房屋\Nmay continue to keep light in our homes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:07.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}照亮我們的街道 為工業機器提供燃料\Ncity streets safe from sin in the night, fuel the machines of industry,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.84,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}推動我們偉大的國家前進\Ndrive our great nation forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:16.44,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們文明種族進步 我們祈禱\Nas our noble species evolves. In Your name, we pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:28.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}現在是幾月\NSo, what month is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:32.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}年末了 我們是最後一批出海的船隻了\NOh, late in the year, we were one of the last ships to go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:35.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}也是為什麼我和我朋友巴爾齊萊有臥鋪\NWhich is why my friend Barzillai and I got a berth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:40.65,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}聽著 我當時14歲\NLook, I was fourteen... fourteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:44.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}尼克森 別站著 幹活\NNickerson, you're standin' around, boy! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:48.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}第一次出海 很害怕 更害怕顯露出來\NFirst time at sea, scared, more scared to show it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}巴爾齊萊當時17歲\NBarzillai was seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:54.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}在碼頭長大的孤兒都等不及被別人視作大人\NOrphans, grew up on the wharf, both in a hurry to be called men.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:17:00.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你們慢騰騰幹嘛 裝船 快 快\NWhat are you all guys waiting for? Get it aboard! C'mon! Haul away...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.03,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們戴的是飾針是什麼\NWhat are those pins they're wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那些是白鯨徽章 湯姆斯\NThose are whale pins, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我怎麼才能得到一個\NHow do I get one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:09.05,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你得用長矛刺殺一頭白鯨\NWell, you've gotta thrust a killing lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:11.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那是世界上最大的怪物\NThe largest beast ever to breathe on the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:15.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}尼克森 把那綠色的東西給邦德先生\NNickerson, get the green stuff to Mr. Bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:18.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}快點 媽的\NMake it quick, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:21.70,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我總有一天會有一堆那東西\NI shall have twelve of those one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}把它們放到匣子裏\NPut 'em on the Grandira casket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:30.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你也上船就說明一件事\NWell, well, you being on board means only one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:34.50,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是啊 這船上至少有一人明白歐文·查斯是誰\NYep! At least there's one person on this ship who knows the truth about Owen Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:37.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 可惜其他的船都已經滿員了\NNo, but all the other ships have already crewed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:42.17,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不不 我洗心革面了 歐文 問題是你呢\NNo, no, I'm a reformed man, Owen, the question is are YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.59,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}別告訴我花花公子馬修戒酒了\NDon't tell me Matthew Joy has put down the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:48.20,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我有罪 歐文·查斯能消消他的壞脾氣了嗎\NI have sinned. Has Owen Chase put down his temper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:50.09,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}平靜的像教堂\NSerene as the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}照我看來\NI'll believe THAT when I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:58.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}考慮到我們的船長 我覺得你只能平靜一小會兒\NGiven our captain I'll give your serenity about 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:00.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}祝你好運\NGood luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:10.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德 喬治·波拉德 歐文·查斯\N- Pollard, George Pollard. - Owen Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:15.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯 你父親的名字對嗎 對 是的\N- Chase, your father's name, isn't it? - Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:19.97,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}馬上他要離開島一段時間而我舒適得待在家\NVery shortly he will be off island for some time and I'll be very much at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:26.36,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我要說 我有點意外 通常船長可以選擇自己的大副\NI say, I was surprised, normally a captain gets to choose his first mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:28.78,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果是有經驗的船長的話 是的\NAn experienced captain, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}當人 你可以理解老頭的意思\NOf course, you can understand from the owners' point of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們想讓自己的財產在適合的人手裏\Nthey wanted to put their investments in the hands of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:34.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}確實\NIndeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:37.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們也許想要多些保障\NThey probably wanted a little extra reassurance, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:41.05,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}看著點我 如果我做錯什麼了告訴我\NWell, DO keep an eye on me, let me know if I'm doing anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:43.38,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不會遲疑的 船長\NI'd have it not other way, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:56.36,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}起錨\NShore up the anchor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:58.60,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}起風了 頂部橫桿放下了嗎 好\N- Head's in the wind, is the top rail off? - Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:00.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}克拉德 掌舵 好\N- Collard, Take the helm! - Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:01.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}花花公子 揚帆\NMr. Joy, make sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:03.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}科爾 查普爾 守在起錨器旁\NMr. Cole, Mr. Chappel, stand by this anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查普爾 掌舵\NMr. Chappel, take the helm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:32.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼帆布還沒有鬆開\NBoyd! Why aren't those braces laid out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:48.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}打開帆 媽的\NSet the sail, god damn it!
