Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}幹的漂亮 查斯\NNice piece of work, Mr. Chase!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果兩周內能到佛得角\NIf we make Cape Verdes in the next 2 weeks we'll
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:25.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們有很大幾率能按時到太平洋\Nhave a decent chance of reaching the Pacific on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:30.44,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}玉米棒 查斯\NCorn, Mr. Chase?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:33.74,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不需要 謝謝 從來不喜歡\NNo, thank you, Sir, never did have much of a taste for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:36.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}太怪了\NThat's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:40.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你爸在科德角是種玉米的吧 是的\N- So, your father grew corn on Cape Cod. - That's right, he did.
