Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:52.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}種玉米 秋葵 大豆 然後他進了監獄\NCorn, okra, beans, I believe? Before he went to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:57.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}花花公子 聽起來熟悉嗎\NAre you familiar with this story, Mr. Joy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:04.60,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你知道查斯是因為他的父親進監獄才變成孤兒的嗎\NWere you aware that Mr. Chase was effectively orphaned due to his father's incarceration?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:08.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們都有不同的經歷\NWell, we all have our paths to sea.
