Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.91,0:22:29.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}或者提醒我不是他們一家人了\Nor off-islander by some Nantucket reminding me how I am NOT part of their family.
