Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:40.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查普爾 長官\N- Mr. Chappel. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:42.16,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長魚叉手\NCaptain's harpooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.36,0:23:45.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}勞倫斯 你做我的 遵命 長官\N- Mr. Lawrence, you'll be mine. - Aye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:50.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}彼得森 二副的魚叉手\NAnd Mr. Peterson, second mate's harpooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.81,0:23:51.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}遵命 長官\NAye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:56.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一船上六人 首要一點要警覺\NThere'll be six men to a boat, first rules in the row, six bells sharp.
