Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.82,0:24:26.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒關係 我不關心 我對你們的要求只有一個\NThat's fine, I don't give a damn, but we interred you for just one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:31.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}只有一個 就是鯨油\Nand one thing only, and that is whale oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.67,0:24:35.58,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我要裝滿2000桶油並盡快回家\NI intend to fill our 2000 barrels and be home as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.79,0:24:39.38,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}即使天氣好而且沒有鯨出沒 克芬先生\NAnd even when the weather is fine and there ARE no whales, Mr. Coffin,
