Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.73,0:24:49.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}明白 長官\N- Aye, sir. Aye, Sir. - Aye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.59,0:24:57.16,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}小子 上甲板\NGreen horn, on deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.01,0:25:01.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}走\NOn ya go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.11,0:25:06.48,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}遵命 遵命 陸人\NAye, aye, landsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.58,0:25:09.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}湯姆·尼克森 對吧 是的 長官\N- Thomas Nickerson, right? - Aye, Sir.
