Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.94,0:25:26.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}好點了嗎\NBetter now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.11,0:25:33.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}長官 非常對不起\NSir, I am so sorry.
