Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.33,0:25:44.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我母親葬在史密斯山\NMy mother's buried up in Smith's Hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.19,0:25:47.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我爸也是 他\Nand a stone for my father, too, he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.67,0:25:50.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他在我出生前就葬身大海了\Nhe was lost at sea before I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.40,0:25:53.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}給我\NHere, give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.67,0:25:59.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}白鯨現在是你的家人了 是好是壞\NThe whale's is your family now, Boy, for better or for worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.89,0:26:03.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}壞處多是\NFor worse mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.14,0:26:08.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}清理甲板 小子\NSwab the deck, Kid!
