Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.26,0:26:27.89,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是 長官\NAye, aye, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.99,0:26:31.74,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你系錯繩子了 是 長官\N- You got that line wrong, Nickerson. - Aye, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.79,0:26:34.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果有必要我們會訓練到日落\NWe'll stay at this until sunlight if we have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.35,0:26:35.43,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是 長官\NAye, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.63,0:26:37.95,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}魚叉手準備乘船\NHarpooners make ready to boat.
