Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.98,0:27:07.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}幹的不錯 雷\NNot bad, Mr. Ray, well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.08,0:27:11.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}要習慣 夥計們 你們得像馬一樣工作\NGet used to it, mates, you gotta work like horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.40,0:27:13.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生 長官\N- Mr. Chase. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.85,0:27:16.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}揚帆\NSet stuns'ls.
