Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.60,0:27:29.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}揚帆\NSet stuns'ls.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.76,0:27:36.24,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}揚帆\NSet stuns'ls.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.28,0:27:39.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拴繩 揚帆\NBelay that, set stuns'ls.
