Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.41,0:27:43.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}遵命 長官\NAye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.63,0:28:28.66,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}她老了 但是還能讓我們爽 哈哈\NShe might be old but she can still blow, boys!
