Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.18,0:28:44.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}還不行 查斯\NNot just yet, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.44,0:28:46.70,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}長官 我們以8里的速度駛向風暴\NSir, we are headed into a storm of more than 8 knots
