Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.67,0:28:59.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果我們不降帆並駛離 風暴一定會追上我們的\NIf we don't shorten sail and bear off it'll catch us on the beam.
