Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.09,0:29:07.34,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}勞倫斯 繼續向前 繼續向前 長官\N- Mr. Lawrence, hold our course. - Holding course, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.50,0:29:09.34,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們這樣前行會追到只差半天的航程\NWe'll lose half a day running like that.
