Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.40,0:29:49.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}準備好應付天氣 邦德 我們要駛向風暴了\NBest prepare for weather, Mr. Bond, we're headed into a squall.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.82,0:30:12.32,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們必須降帆離開這裏 退下 查斯先生\N- We must fall off and run with it. - Stand down, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.42,0:30:16.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}勞倫斯 航向不變 航向不變 長官\N- Mr. Lawrence, hold your course. - Holding course, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.34,0:30:34.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}降帆 查斯\NShorten the sails, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.98,0:30:42.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們要砍下那些帆\NWe need to cut those sails down!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.07,0:31:02.78,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船掉頭 向陸地開\NTurn the ship, head for land!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.83,0:31:05.97,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 損壞已經造成了\NNo, the damage is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.83,0:31:11.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}太晚了 太他媽晚了\NIt's too late, it's too god damned late!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.06,0:31:14.09,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們會撞上的\NWe'll be broadsided!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.22,0:31:34.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}抓牢\NHold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.62,0:32:05.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}小心\NLook out!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.61,0:32:28.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}花花公子\NMr. Joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.43,0:32:31.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們要割斷 我知道了 歐文\N- We have to cut away the... - I've got it, Owen!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.54,0:32:33.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們要讓船擺正\NWe have to set her up right!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.98,0:33:28.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你說要見我 長官\NYou wish to see me, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.48,0:33:34.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}明天六時 你召集船員\NAt six bells tomorrow, you will assemble the crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.13,0:33:38.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}告知他們我們將返回楠塔基特維修\Ninform them that we will be returning to Nantucket for repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.12,0:33:42.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後你向他們道歉你干涉了船長的命令\NYou will then apologize to them for interfering with a captain's order
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.40,0:33:45.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}今天差點讓船上的每個人都為此喪命\Nwhich nearly cost the lives of every man on this ship today.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.14,0:33:46.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}什麼\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.74,0:33:49.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}返回到港口我會接受你的辭呈\NI'll accept your resignation upon our return to port.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.75,0:33:51.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}就這些\NThat will be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.35,0:33:53.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是你下命令楊帆的 長官\NIt was your order to set stuns'ls, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.10,0:33:55.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}命令沒問題 這些人需要鍛煉\NThat decision was sound, the men needed testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.99,0:33:58.05,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你送他們進風暴\N- You sent 'em into a storm? - That...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.25,0:33:59.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那是幸運不好\Nwas unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.88,0:34:03.91,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 這是缺乏航海經驗 責怪運氣只會顯得軟弱\NNo, it was bad seamanship, and blaming misfortune is just plain weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.01,0:34:08.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你他媽的無禮 你知道你在和誰說話嗎\NDamn your impertinence! Do you know who you're speaking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.21,0:34:12.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我是船長喬治·波拉德 波拉德\NMy name is CAPTAIN George Pollard. POLLARD!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.37,0:34:19.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}而你查斯先生 無論你衣袖上釘多少白鯨徽章\NAnd you Mr. Chase, no matter how many whale pins you may have on your lapel,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.64,0:34:21.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你不過是個農民的兒子\Nare nothing more than the son of a farmer,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.00,0:34:25.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}仗勢欺人才當上的長官\Nwho's managed to bullying his way into an officer's tunic.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.49,0:34:28.38,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}滾出去\NNow, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.13,0:34:35.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不帶一桶油回港口是個錯誤 長官\NTo return to port without a single barrel of oil would be a mistake, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.16,0:34:41.16,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}和名字是波拉德或者查斯沒什麼關係\NAnd not behoove a man whose name is Pollard... or Chase, for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.36,0:34:45.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}對我們來說最好是抓緊時間工作\NAnd the best thing for both of us would be t'work all hours God sends us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.83,0:34:48.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}把船裝滿油一年之內回到家\NFill this ship with oil, and be home inside a year
