Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.37,0:34:57.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}相信我 我也迫不及待這樣做\NTrust me, I have never been as desirous of that as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.80,0:35:03.59,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}當然 這由船長來做決定\NOf course, that is the Captain's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.35,0:35:16.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們像一對新婚夫婦\NThey were like a new married couple.
