Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.78,0:35:24.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但新婚夫婦也能兩敗俱傷\Nbut a new married couple can also bring down a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.62,0:35:28.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你結婚了嗎 梅爾維爾先生 是的\N- You married, Mr. Melville? - I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.37,0:35:30.34,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}上帝仁慈\NThe Lord have mercy on ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.23,0:35:32.58,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}第一個孩子也快生了\NFirst child on the way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.71,0:35:36.73,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那你的妻子知道你把所有的積蓄都帶來了\NSo, does your good wife know that you brought all you have in the world here tonight,
