Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.93,0:36:02.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}Ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.76,0:36:05.60,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}噴水\NBlows!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.06,0:36:09.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是大傢伙 噴水了\NA big one! Thar she blows!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.18,0:36:14.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}公的母的 拉姆斯德爾先生  他們是公的\N- White or sperm, Mr. Ramsdell? - Sperm whales they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.12,0:36:18.38,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生  升起船隻\NMr. Chase, hoist and swing boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.51,0:36:22.78,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}都來甲板\N- All Hands! All hands on deck! - All hands on deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.17,0:36:31.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}放船\NLower away!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.17,0:36:40.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}出海三個月 南大西洋
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.70,0:37:17.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}再加把勁兒\NCome on, put your back into it.!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.31,0:37:29.24,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}幼年鯨\NThere's the calf.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.32,0:37:35.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}幼年鯨 母鯨\N- That's the calf? - That's the cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.15,0:37:48.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}乖乖 那是我們的錢\NThat's our boy! That's the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.13,0:37:51.17,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}尼克森 使勁\NNickerson! Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.57,0:37:54.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}夠四十桶油了吧 五十桶\N- Forty barrels there? - Fifty!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.31,0:37:57.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}天 他是個大傢伙\NBoy, he's a buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.31,0:38:01.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}使勁劃 要不然他要逃了\NTake the oars, lads! Quick or he'll god damn run!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.66,0:38:05.48,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}劃起來 機靈點 夥計們 機靈點\NPull those oars up! Smartly, lads, smartly!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.03,0:38:07.78,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}小心槳端\NMind your oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.47,0:38:11.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拉姆斯德爾 準備繩 是 長官\N- Mr. Ramsdell, prepare the line. - Aye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.27,0:38:16.89,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}第一頭是我的\NThe first one's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.49,0:38:20.16,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}瞄準她的弱點\NAim her to the free spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.11,0:38:23.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拉 拉 跟著\NPull! Pull! Stay on him.
