Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.38,0:39:02.50,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}地球上最可怕的生物\NThe most fearsome creature to ever live on this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.68,0:39:18.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我的手\NMy hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.16,0:39:28.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你得把繩弄濕 尼克森\NYou need to wet the line, Nickerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.85,0:39:43.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}只剩140英尋的繩子了 查斯先生\NA hundred forty fathoms' of line left, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.37,0:39:54.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}只剩80英尋的繩子了 長官\NEighty fathoms' of line left, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.74,0:40:01.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他會把我們拖到水裏的\NHe's gonna pull us under!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.56,0:40:06.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}馬修 我要你的繩子 給我繩\N- Matthew, I need your line! - Feed the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.39,0:40:08.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}彼得森給我繩子 是的 長官\N- Peterson give me the line! - Aye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.44,0:40:13.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}把那繩給我 彼得森 我們只剩60英尋的繩子了 長官\N- Give me that line, Mr. Peterson. - We're down to 60 fathoms' of line left, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.52,0:40:18.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}20英尋了 查斯先生 鬆開繩\N- Twenty fathoms, Mr. Chase! - Tie it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.72,0:40:24.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}快\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.01,0:40:39.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}彼得森 你來 是 長官\N- Peterson, lay on! - Aye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.87,0:40:42.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}還剩多長的繩子\NHow many fathoms can he draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.06,0:40:48.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 不 等等\NNo, no, no, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.41,0:40:55.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}歐文 不 不是現在\N- Owen! - Oh, no, not yet!
