Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.30,0:43:02.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}滾開 混賬畜生\NGet out of there, you sons of bitches!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.94,0:43:08.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}- 你拿到了嗎 拿到了 查斯\N- You got it? - Got it, Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.09,0:43:13.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}看起來怎麼樣 不怎麼樣\N- How's it lookin'? - Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.38,0:43:17.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}就這麼多了\NThat's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.46,0:43:23.95,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生 什麼\N- Mr. Chase, Sir? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.00,0:43:26.38,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}長官 就這麼多了 我們拿不到更多了\NThat's all of it, Sir, we can't get anymore out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.50,0:43:29.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那就是金礦 夥計們 繼續挖\NThat's the gold in there, Boys, c'mon, keep diggin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.38,0:43:33.32,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我塊頭太大下不去 得找個身材小的\N- I'm too big to really go down there. - Then find someone who can.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.64,0:43:40.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}尼克森 過來小子\NNickerson, come here boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.90,0:43:45.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿 我喊你過來\NHey! I said c'mere!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.37,0:43:50.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}爬進去\NClimb on in with 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.99,0:43:52.28,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}來啊 湯姆斯\NCome on, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.78,0:43:56.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這裏面的東西可比它的肉值錢多了\NWhat's in there is worth a HELLEVA lot more than what they're boilin' down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.51,0:44:06.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}長官 我不行 對不起 我做不了\NSir, I can't, I'm sorry. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.31,0:44:09.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你自己進去或者我讓你睡在裏面\NYou get down there, or I'll have you sleep down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.83,0:44:14.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你用牙齒把這東西咬住 小子\NYou best put that between your teeth, Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.68,0:44:17.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}它裏面臭得很\NIt tastes worse than the Devil's asshole down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.01,0:44:22.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.50,0:44:31.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}抱歉 尼克森 我的枕頭送你\N- Sorry. - Here, Nickerson, take my pillow with ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.87,0:44:35.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}下去\NDown ya go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.17,0:44:54.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一個人在裏面能更瞭解自己\NA man gets to know himself down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.56,0:45:01.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們有送你進一頭鯨的頭裏面嗎 沒有 他們饒了我\N- Did they ever send you into a whale's head? - No, I was spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.86,0:45:04.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那裏面才是寶藏所在\NWell, that's where the treasure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.71,0:45:08.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我永遠都不會忘記那第一頭\NI'll never forget that first bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.37,0:45:15.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}47桶油 當然 幸福很短暫\NForty-seven barrels... of course, the happiness was short lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.32,0:45:17.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那片水域沒有鯨魚可捕了\NThe waters had all been fished out?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.91,0:45:23.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是的 所以我們向更遠處前進\NThat they had. So, we headed further out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.19,0:45:29.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}在那一個月之後\NIt was a month around the Horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.09,0:45:34.24,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}離開了南大西洋\NLeft the South Atlantic behind with a sliver of hope
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.29,0:45:36.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}期望情況會變好\Nthat things would change for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.28,0:45:41.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但到了太平洋事實上沒有改善\NBut making the Pacific didn't improve our lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.78,0:45:46.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}太他媽難看到鯨了\NWhale sightings were TOO damn scarce.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.80,0:45:52.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}將近一年後脾氣衝動的船長\NAfter nearly a year at sea the temperaments of our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.58,0:45:55.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}和大副都變的沮喪\NAnd our first mate grew more strained.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.13,0:46:00.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長波拉德幾乎整天待在船艙裏\NCaptain Pollard spent most days and nights in his cabin,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.89,0:46:03.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}害怕看到船員無法交代\Nafraid to look his crew in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.47,0:46:10.89,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們的倉儲大半還空著\NOur hold was almost empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.71,0:46:17.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}凝視著我們皮毛的成果只會提醒我們\NTo gaze upon our paltry efforts only served as a reminder
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.32,0:46:20.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}離回家還有很長一段路\Nthat we were a long way from going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.32,0:46:36.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}阿塔卡梅斯 厄瓜多爾
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.86,0:46:47.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我聽不懂 說英語\NI don't talk that talk. Speak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.95,0:46:53.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們在說鯨油\NThey're talking whale oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.95,0:47:17.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}牧師堅持要我們寫信回家告知我們的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.07,0:47:18.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他覺得這些信幫得了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.57,0:47:20.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那些寡婦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.57,0:47:21.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船都沒有的船主
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.87,0:47:25.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你還要像這樣生活多久 船長
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.07,0:47:33.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}寫信給西班牙 為你和你的船長 祈求原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.97,0:47:37.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒人可以阻止發生的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.57,0:47:41.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}誰會相信呢 沒有人 顧主不會相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.67,0:47:46.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這麼多年你用油換來錢裝滿他們的口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.29,0:47:49.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}長官\NCapitбn.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.09,0:47:53.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}打擾了 當地人告訴我你的航程遇到阻礙了 長官\NExcuse me, the locals told me that your voyage was waylaid, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.39,0:47:56.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號船長 喬治·波拉德\NCaptain George Pollard, the Essex.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.00,0:48:00.43,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}聖瑪麗亞號船長 克萊門特佩萊斯\NCapitбn Clemente Pelaez, the Santa Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.89,0:48:03.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}給大伙來一杯\NWould you buy a colleague a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.24,0:48:06.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}老樣子 喬治 是的 船長\N- Same as always, George. - Yes, Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.24,0:48:13.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}壞運氣\NBad luck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.36,0:48:16.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那有多遠\NHow far out?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.51,0:48:18.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}遠到只有傻子才會去\NFar enough for only a fool to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.05,0:48:20.45,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那是多遠\NHow far would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.57,0:48:24.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一千里格 在赤道附近\NA thousand leagues along the Equator...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.35,0:48:26.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}近海區域\Nin offshore grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.89,0:48:29.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}鯨都在那兒\NWere there whales there?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.40,0:48:32.09,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}多到你做夢不敢想\NMore than you've ever dreamt.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.69,0:48:36.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}成百上千 密密麻麻望不到邊\NHundreds... fields of flukes as far as the eye can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.39,0:48:40.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們原本一天就夠裝滿3000桶油\NThey could fill up 3000 barrels in the space of a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.66,0:48:42.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}什麼意思 "原本"\NWhat do you mean, "Could have"?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.26,0:48:49.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}要不是那裏的那頭怪物\NIf it weren't for that demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.69,0:48:52.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一頭鯨\Na whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.98,0:48:55.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}白如蠟石\NWhite as alabaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.28,0:48:57.05,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一百英尺長\Na hundred feet long,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.32,0:49:01.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我的六名船員因為它喪命\Nsent six of my crew to their graves,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.59,0:49:13.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}剩下的我們 只會讓人想起那頭怪物\Nand the rest of us, something to remember him by.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.30,0:49:18.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那頭白鯨 他跳舞給你看 還逗你玩嗎\NNow, this white whale, did he dance a jig and pick your pocket, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.33,0:49:25.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.37,0:49:29.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你相信他的鬼話\NDo you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.83,0:49:35.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們馬上出發 趕上南風帶\NWe set sail now, catch the south easterlies,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.92,0:49:39.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這是我們絕佳的機會 填飽肚子 我們有機會在半年內回家\Nthis is by our best time, fill our belly, we can be home in six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.21,0:49:42.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你怎麼看 查斯先生\NWhat say you, Mr. Chase?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.22,0:49:46.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒必要再忍受這種困境了\NNo need to endure our predicament for a moment longer than necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.62,0:49:47.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}同意\NAmen to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.05,0:49:50.34,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}同意\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.30,0:49:54.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}貪婪影響了船長和大副\NGreed took hold of our Captain and the first mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.30,0:49:59.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後我們沿著赤道前往一千里格外的\NSo, we headed out... a thousand leagues along the Equator...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.61,0:50:04.60,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是沒想到 傳言流開了\Nbut with no agenda, speculation began.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.41,0:50:07.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}說鯨都藏在那裏\NThis is where the whales are gonna hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.10,0:50:10.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那是我們能到達的最遠的地方\NIt was as far from land as we could possibly go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.42,0:50:13.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是我們要追捕他們\NBut we hunted them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.29,0:50:18.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}幾個世紀前 水手們害怕會航到地球邊界\NCenturies before, sailors feared sailing off the edge of the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.88,0:50:23.36,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但我們是駛向理智的邊緣\Nbut we were headed for the edge of sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.50,0:50:30.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}信任給猜疑讓位\NTrust gave way to doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.73,0:50:33.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}期望消除迷信\Nhope to blind superstition.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.97,0:50:36.09,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長 船員在議論\NCap'n, the men are talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.19,0:50:38.48,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這很正常\NThat's what men do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.53,0:50:41.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們對你航行這麼遠的決定不滿\NThey aren't happy with your decision to sail out this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.34,0:50:43.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你糾正他們的觀點了嗎\NWell, did you correct them?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.32,0:50:47.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你提醒他們我們的目標是用鯨油裝滿這艘船\NDid you remind them of our purpose to fill this ship with whale oil
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.15,0:50:50.24,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果那裏有成百上千頭鯨 為什麼不去呢\Nand if the whales ARE a thousand leagues out, then that is where we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.36,0:50:56.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}表哥 拜託了 這太瘋狂了\NCousin, please, this is madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.08,0:51:01.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你被那人影響了\NYou have let yourself be influenced by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.32,0:51:02.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你必須把船調頭\NYou must turn this ship back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.64,0:51:09.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我建議你回去 消除他們的疑慮\NI suggest you go back down, reassure the men, the leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.36,0:51:14.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}以後別再仗著家庭身份來找我\Nand don't ever, ever abuse the privilege of family with me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.65,0:51:18.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}克芬先生\NMr. Coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.65,0:51:31.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}出海第十四個月
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.40,0:51:49.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}怎麼了\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.47,0:51:52.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}聽 查斯先生\N- Listen... - Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.28,0:51:54.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我看到些白柱 哪裏\N- I see some white water. - Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.22,0:51:55.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}左舷\NPort side!
