Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.66,1:11:41.79,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 不 不 讓我看看\N- No, no, no. - Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.84,1:11:42.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我沒事 我沒事\NI'm fine, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.90,1:11:45.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}放鬆 我知道 讓我看一眼\NJust relax, I know, I know, let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.25,1:11:53.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我被擊中頭部了 我沒事 好嗎\NI'm hit on the head, it's good, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.86,1:11:56.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}給他些水 我不需要什麼水\N- Give him some water! - I don't need any water!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.17,1:11:58.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}給他他媽的一些水喝\NGive him some God damned water.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.11,1:12:00.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 不 我不需要水 我沒事\NNo, no, no, I don't need water, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.75,1:12:10.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拿著\NTake that, take it!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.84,1:12:13.38,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒事\NI gotcha, I gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.48,1:12:16.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒事的 你會沒事的\NAll right, you'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.97,1:12:22.97,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿 你們在看什麼 我沒事\NHey, what are you all looking at, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.32,1:12:25.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德船長 我裝的\NCap'n Pollard, this is fiddle.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.27,1:12:28.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我忽悠你們的 聽見了嗎\NThis is God damn fiddle, ya hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.41,1:12:30.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}歐文 在\N- Owen. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.59,1:12:33.59,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我沒事 我沒事\NI'm fine, all right, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.98,1:12:37.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我沒事 離開這\N- Thank you. - I'm fine! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.49,1:12:39.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他沒事\NHe is good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.82,1:12:41.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.56,1:12:46.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼在死人身上浪費水\NWhy waste water on a dead man?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.68,1:12:51.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們從小一起航海 情同手足\NFancy men who know each other, sailed together since childhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.87,1:12:53.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你告訴我\NNow, tell me,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.30,1:12:56.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你會坐等著看你的兄弟死去嗎\Ncould you just sit there and watch your own brother die?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.20,1:13:00.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}簡單的算術問題 查普爾先生\NIt's simply a matter of numbers, Mr. Chappel.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.86,1:13:02.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}水不夠我們所有人用\NThere's not enough for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.76,1:13:17.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼在死人身上浪費水\NWhy waste water on a dead man?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.41,1:13:19.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼浪費水\NWhy waste water...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.83,1:13:22.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼浪費水\NWhy waste water?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.01,1:13:25.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼在死人身上浪費水\NWhy waste water on a dead man?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.70,1:13:27.91,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}尼克森先生\NMr. Nickerson?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.30,1:13:31.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼在死人身上浪費水 你還好嗎 先生\N- Why waste water on a dead man? - Are you all right, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.09,1:13:34.59,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不能 不能什麼\N- I cannot. - Cannot what?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.64,1:13:38.84,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 你 你 你知道足夠多了 你瞭解夠多了\NNo, you... you... you have enough, you have more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.89,1:13:40.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是 先生 我們都講到這兒了\NBut, Sir! We've come so far.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.41,1:13:43.71,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們必須善始善終 我們有約定的 先生\N- We have come to an end. - We have an agreement, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.76,1:13:46.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拿著錢離開 這是魔鬼的交易\NTake the money and leave! You've a devil's bargain!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.12,1:13:50.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 長官 魔鬼喜歡隱藏秘密\NNo, Sir, the devil loves his unspoken secrets...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.20,1:13:56.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}特別是那些蠶食人的靈魂的秘密\Nespecially those that fester in a man's soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.81,1:14:00.36,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你的秘密是什麼\NWhat's yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.47,1:14:21.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不是一個好作家\NI'm not a great writer.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.49,1:14:26.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不是霍索恩\NI'm not Hawthorne.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.28,1:14:29.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}從我學寫作以來\NAfter my first hearing of Odysseus,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.14,1:14:32.08,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這個故事一直困擾著我\Nthis tale has haunted me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.87,1:14:35.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}它消耗著我\NIt consumes me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.90,1:14:38.74,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我害怕如果我不寫這個故事\NI fear if I do not write it,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.70,1:14:42.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我會再也沒辦法寫作\NI should never write again.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.93,1:14:45.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}還有什麼\NWhat else?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.10,1:14:49.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我害怕如果我寫這個故事\NI fear if I DO write it,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.63,1:14:53.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}寫出來的不如故事精彩\Nthat it will not be as good as it should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.75,1:15:05.79,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}繼續講這個故事 先生\NContinue the story, Sir...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.71,1:15:08.52,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為了彼此\Nfor the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.71,1:15:20.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}困住的第34天
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.94,1:15:26.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}傳過去\NPass that down.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.57,1:15:32.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}給\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.26,1:15:41.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們感謝你 主 賜予我們的食物\NWe thank thee, Lord, for this is our food...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.75,1:15:47.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}賜予我們的光 健康 和所有美好的東西\Nfor light, good health, with every good.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.13,1:15:49.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那裏\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.00,1:15:51.03,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}陸地\NLand!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.24,1:15:54.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}陸地 歐文 陸地\NLand, Owen! Land!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.97,1:15:57.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}陸地 陸地 陸地\NLand! Land! Land!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.58,1:16:00.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}划船 快\NRow! Get 'way! Get 'way!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.60,1:16:05.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}划船\NRow!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.35,1:16:27.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}停下 停下 停下\NHold fast! Hold fast! Hold fast!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.68,1:16:30.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯 什麼東西 長官\NMr.Chase, what is it, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.60,1:16:34.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯 那是什麼怪物 你怎麼停下了\NMr. Chase, what the devil is it, why have you stopped?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.26,1:16:36.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他一直在跟著我們 什麼\N- He's been following us. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.38,1:16:39.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那裏什麼都沒有 查斯先生\NThere's nothin' out there, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.80,1:16:41.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那裏什麼都沒有 長官\NThere ain't nothin' out there, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.51,1:16:43.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}長官 你在幹什麼\NSir, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.91,1:17:27.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他在哪兒\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.72,1:19:30.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這可能是迪西島\NIt could be Ducie Island.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.40,1:19:34.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒有地圖 指南針 象限儀 沒辦法確認\NWithout a map, compass or quadrant there's no way to be certain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.75,1:19:36.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們晝夜都亮著火\NWe will keep fires going night and day,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.46,1:19:40.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但願過往的船隻注意到我們的濃煙\Nhope a passing ship catches sight of our smoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.52,1:20:39.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這是我想讓你們看的\NThis is what I wanted you to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.86,1:20:50.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們肯定在這很長時間了\NThey've been here a long time, for no doubt...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.26,1:20:52.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一定也在等船隻\Nwaiting for a ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.96,1:20:55.24,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是沒有船來過\NBut no ship came.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.87,1:20:59.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒有船會來\NNo ship is going to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.63,1:21:02.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果我們呆在這 我們會死\NIf we stay, we die.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.09,1:21:05.24,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你們覺得如果鳥兒過來看到\NHow long do you think it would take to trust the birds
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.31,1:21:07.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}自己的蛋被吃了會多久不再過來\Nto stop coming here once they see their eggs eaten?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.62,1:21:30.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這是知道自己將要死去的好處\NIt's a privilege to know the moment of one's death in advance.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.69,1:21:32.48,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}可以為此準備\NAnd to be able to prepare for it...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.77,1:21:36.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}離家太遠的詛咒\Na curse to be so far from home...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.99,1:21:42.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}或者有機會說再見但沒機會和解\Nor a chance to say goodbyes, without a chance to make peace...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.08,1:21:45.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}或者報仇的機會\Nor a chance to settle scores.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.32,1:21:51.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是 我們之間清楚了\NBut alas, at least those are settled between us,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.49,1:21:52.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長\NCap'n?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.86,1:21:56.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}什麼船長\NCaptain of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.03,1:21:59.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號沉沒了不是你的責任\NThe Essex was lost and no fault o'yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.95,1:22:02.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我該受譴責 你不是船長\N- I was as much to blame... - You were not the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.92,1:22:10.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你天生就是幹這活的料\NYou were born to do this job.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.06,1:22:13.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我只是生下來只能幹這個\NI was just born into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.90,1:22:27.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們幹了什麼 你覺得 喬治\NWhat we do, do ya think, George?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.53,1:22:33.60,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們幹了什麼冒犯了上帝 讓他這麼不開心\NWhat offense did we give God to upset him so?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.65,1:22:36.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}冒犯上帝的是那些白鯨\NThe only creature to have offended God here is the whale.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.35,1:22:38.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不是我們\NNot us?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.45,1:22:44.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不是我們的傲慢 我們的貪婪 看我們現在在哪兒\NNot our arrogance, our greed? Look where we find ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.12,1:22:46.65,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們是上帝按自己喜好創造出來的高級生物\NWe are supreme creatures made in God's own likeness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.05,1:22:49.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們是地球上的主宰\NWe're earthly kings,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.93,1:22:53.73,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們要環航我們居住的星球\Nwhose business it is to circumnavigate the planet bestowed to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.32,1:22:56.48,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}將自然屈服於我們的意志\NAnd to bend nature to OUR will.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.59,1:23:00.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們經歷了這麼多你還覺得主宰一切嗎\NYou really feel like an earthly king after everything that we've been through?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.63,1:23:06.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們什麼都不是 我們是微粒 灰塵 但是我們\N- We're nothing... we're specks... dust. - But we're...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.14,1:23:09.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拂曉時朝太陽方向行駛\NWe sail into the sun at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.56,1:23:14.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果我們要死 死在上帝的光輝裏\NIf we are to die, with God's grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.20,1:23:17.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}讓我們像男人一樣死去\NLet us die as men.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.51,1:23:31.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們準備好了嗎 維克斯先生 是的 長官\N- Are we ready, Mr. Weeks? - Aye, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.64,1:23:40.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查普爾先生\NMr. Chappel.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.40,1:23:43.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}萊特先生 我不能 長官\N- Mr. Wright. - I can't do it, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.14,1:23:45.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我 洛克斯 維克斯\NMe, Locks and Weeks...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.18,1:23:48.66,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們留下來\Nwe're stayin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.18,1:23:58.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}準備出發 馬修\NReady to go, Matthew?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.67,1:24:12.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我來幫你一把 有什麼用\N- I'll give you a hand here... - What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.54,1:24:14.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你聽見我說的嗎 不 我們一起回家 一起回家\N- You hear me? - No, we're goin' home, we're goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.77,1:24:16.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒用的\NThere's no point.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.96,1:24:18.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}走吧\NJust go.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.22,1:24:24.44,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}媽的 馬修\NGod damn it, Matthew.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.14,1:24:28.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒事的\NIt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.51,1:24:31.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我回家立馬派一艘船過來接你\NI'll send a boat for you the minute we get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.82,1:24:34.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後我們回到楠塔基特玩牌 好嗎\NAnd we'll play cards back in Nantucket, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.75,1:24:37.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}好 一言為定 好\N- Yeah, it's a deal. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.51,1:24:46.43,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你要我幫你打開水壺嗎\NYou want me to open that for ya?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.43,1:24:52.58,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我能行的\NNaw, I think I'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.74,1:25:00.40,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}上帝保佑你 兄弟\NGod be with you, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.21,1:25:04.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}也保佑你\NAnd you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.58,1:25:24.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}彼得森\NBrother Peterson?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.93,1:25:28.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你一起跟我們走吧 彼得森先生\N- Y'all comin' with us? - Mr. Peterson.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.06,1:25:31.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}和邦德一起登船走吧\NWhy don't you come on our boat with Mr. Bond.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.06,1:26:02.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}困住的第48天
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.63,1:26:07.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}在哪兒 他在哪兒\NWhere... where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.22,1:26:09.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德\NPollard.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.74,1:26:13.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}勞倫斯先生 勞倫斯先生 醒醒\NMr. Lawrence, Mr. Lawrence, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.84,1:26:16.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}另一條船去哪兒了\NWhere has the other boat gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.33,1:26:19.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德 波拉德 船長波拉德\N- Pollard! Pollard! - Captain Pollard!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.57,1:26:22.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德 波拉德 船長波拉德\N- Pollard! Pollard! - Cap'n Pollard!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.48,1:26:24.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德 船長\N- Pollard! - Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.63,1:26:31.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}波拉德\NPollard!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.43,1:26:36.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}休息會兒\NGet some rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.64,1:26:54.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}本傑明 你在幹什麼\NBenjamin, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.90,1:26:56.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他死了\NHe's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.01,1:26:58.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}把他丟海裏 長官\NThrowing him overboard, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.54,1:27:03.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}看著我 看著我 本傑明\NLook at me, look at me Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.34,1:27:12.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒有理智的水手會丟棄也許會救自己一命的東西\NNo right minded sailor discards what might yet save him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.35,1:27:25.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}聽我說 孩子 聽我說\NListen to me, Boy, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.72,1:27:31.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他能救我們\NHe can help us.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.97,1:27:34.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我的上帝 我們神聖的\NMy God, our heavenly...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.25,1:27:42.79,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這些生物每日祈盼著食物\NThy creatures wait On Thee for daily food.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.03,1:28:02.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}決定了\NSo it was decided.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.00,1:28:11.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們準備了屍體\NWe prepared the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.06,1:28:16.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們去除了內臟\NWe removed the organs.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.78,1:28:21.28,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}分割了他的四肢\NSeparated his limbs from his body.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.88,1:28:25.91,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}從骨頭上切下了所有的肉\NAnd cut all the flesh from the bones.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.97,1:28:31.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後\NAfter which...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.34,1:28:34.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們拼起了屍塊\Nwe closed body.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.72,1:28:37.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後把屍體縫起來\NAnd then we sewed it up...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.62,1:28:39.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}盡我們所能\Nas decently as we could...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.14,1:28:42.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後扔到了海裏\Nand committed it to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.51,1:28:46.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們先吃了心臟\NWe ate the heart first.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.01,1:28:56.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你有意見\NYou judge me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.62,1:29:00.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.29,1:29:09.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個\NThere... there...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.77,1:29:11.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}說完了\Nit's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.29,1:29:16.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}說完了\NIt is out.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.47,1:29:19.24,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你從未告訴過任何人\NYou never told anyone?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.04,1:29:23.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}沒有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.76,1:29:26.59,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}包括你的妻子\NNot even your wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.39,1:29:29.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你覺得如果她知道我做的罪孽\NDo you think she could ever love me,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.03,1:29:32.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}她還會愛我嗎\Nif she knew the abominations I had committed?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.98,1:29:35.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 她還會愛你的\NYes, she would.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.54,1:29:39.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果你和我相遇的時候告訴我\NAnd if you had told me this story when we met,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.57,1:29:43.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我今天還會是你的妻子\NI would still wear your ring today.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.12,1:29:47.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個男孩的勇敢\NThe strength of that boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.29,1:29:49.58,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}還在你內心\Nstill lives in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.58,1:29:53.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我看得出\NI see that...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.07,1:29:55.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}即使你自己不覺察\Neven if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.15,1:30:19.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你可以說完你的故事了 親愛的\NYou can finish your story now, My Love.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.85,1:30:32.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿\NLook...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.63,1:30:37.70,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}坐起來\NSit up.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.30,1:30:41.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}聽著\NListen.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.71,1:30:44.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}媽的\NDamn thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.15,1:30:49.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們還有些水\NWe still got a few drops of the water left.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.76,1:30:52.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}別放棄 我們要回家了\NDon't ya quit on me, we're goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.01,1:30:59.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你還有家人在嗎\NDo you have a family...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.46,1:31:02.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生\Nback home, Mr. Chase?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.33,1:31:03.71,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}有的 我的妻子\NYeah, I have wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.56,1:31:10.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}對 還有一個兒子和一個女兒\NYes, and a son or a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.56,1:31:27.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}困住的第71天 南美以西1200海里
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.07,1:31:57.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}好\NVery well.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.39,1:32:00.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長 我們重新抽籤\NCap'n, we'll draw again.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.36,1:32:02.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們不會這麼做\NWe'll do no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.60,1:32:06.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們重新抽 拉姆斯德爾先生\N- We'll draw again. - Mr. Ramsdell,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.36,1:32:10.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你要用這槍來指揮\Nyou will assume command of this vessel.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.03,1:32:16.17,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你明白\NYa got that?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.22,1:32:19.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你是我們的船長 你的船員需要你\NYou're our cap'n, your men need you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.61,1:32:22.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船員沒事的\NThe men will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.18,1:32:26.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拜託了 拜託了\NPlease. Please. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.99,1:32:28.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}亨利 讓我們再抽籤\N- Henry... - Let us go again.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.59,1:32:31.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這是命令\NIt is an order.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.63,1:32:34.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果你做不到\NIf you cannot do it,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.63,1:32:36.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}把槍給其他人\Npass the pistol to another man.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.96,1:33:24.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們在赤道無風帶幾周了\NWe were weeks in the Doldrums.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.39,1:33:27.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}太平洋那片區域遠比海洋枯竭\NThat part of the Pacific is more desert than ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.87,1:33:30.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}太陽炙熱\NThe sun beating down...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.81,1:33:32.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我害怕\NMy fear...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.27,1:33:35.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我能想到的是\NAll I could think about...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.76,1:33:40.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}所有人都會死而我是最後一個活著的\Nwas that everyone would die and I'd be the last left alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.75,1:33:46.34,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯只知道我們離陸地還有800英里\NWell, as best as Mr. Chase could tell, we were still 800 miles from land.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.01,1:33:53.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生\NMr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.51,1:34:03.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長波拉德\NCap'n Pollard.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.58,1:34:07.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}很高興見到你\NVery happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.11,1:34:10.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們生存下來沒什麼值得高興\NVery little happiness in our survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.30,1:34:15.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們也是 長官\NNor in ours, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.44,1:34:17.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}巴爾齊萊號\NBarzillai?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.68,1:34:21.03,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}另一艘船\NThe third boat?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.28,1:34:26.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們不見了 幾天不見了\NThey're gone, they've been gone for days.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.99,1:34:29.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我估計他們迷失了 長官\NI'm afraid they're lost, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.07,1:35:01.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生 你為這個準備好了\NMr. Chase, you are prepared for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.97,1:35:19.95,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不過是頭白鯨\NIt's just a whale.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.71,1:35:25.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那裏 投茅\NThere! Throw the lance!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.63,1:35:27.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}投啊\NThrow it!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.70,1:35:34.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}投啊\NThrow it, drown the lad!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.64,1:35:48.32,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}投啊\NThrow it!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.16,1:36:01.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}就是現在 投茅啊\NDo it! Now! Throw the lance!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.51,1:36:22.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你為什麼不投\NWhy didn't you throw it?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.12,1:36:49.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你他媽是個傻子\NYou're a damn fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.04,1:37:15.91,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}洋流把我們拆散了\NThe current drew us apart...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.80,1:37:20.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那是我們最後一次見到船長波拉德的鯨船\Nand that was the last we would see of Captain Pollard's whale boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.80,1:37:23.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}困住的第87天
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.11,1:37:25.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一艘船\NA boat!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.54,1:37:27.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}前方有一艘船\NA boat on the forward bow!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.16,1:37:55.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}上帝仁慈\NMay god have mercy.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.16,1:38:11.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}困住的第90天 1821年2月18日
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.64,1:38:39.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生\NMr. Chase.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.35,1:38:44.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}父親\NFather...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.06,1:38:48.50,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}別丟下我 父親\Ndon't leave me, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.26,1:39:40.40,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿 長官\NHey, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.04,1:39:45.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生 長官 看 看 長官\NMr. Chase. Sir. Look. Look, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.01,1:39:50.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}長官\NSir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.86,1:39:53.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}看 那裏\NLook. Out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.45,1:39:54.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們來了\NThey're coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.81,1:40:01.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們來救我們了\NThey're coming for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.10,1:40:28.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們在那裏被救了\NWe were rescued there, off the Isle of Mбs Afuera, Chile,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.99,1:40:32.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號沉船90天後\Nninety days after the sinking of the Essex.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.40,1:40:37.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們給我們一些衣服和皮革吃\NThey gave us some old clothes... leathers, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.38,1:40:42.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}起先感覺很難吃\NIt was hard to eat at first... strange.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.41,1:40:45.20,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們盡力照顧我們\NThey looked after us as best they could,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.30,1:40:48.50,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後他們找到了可以帶我們回家的一艘船\Nthen we found a ship that could carry us home.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.34,1:40:52.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}回家又花了三個月\NThat voyage took another three months.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.34,1:40:55.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}1821年6月11日 楠塔基特港口
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.70,1:41:04.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}全島的人好像都過來看我們回來\NIt looked like the whole Island turned out to see us return.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.40,1:41:09.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是沒有歡呼 只有沉寂\NBut there were no cheers... only silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.27,1:41:17.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他們看我們的樣子像是看到鬼 幽靈\NThey looked at us like we were... apparitions... phantoms.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.81,1:41:22.07,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們沒有對任何人說起我們生存的細節\NWe'd said nothing of the details of our survival to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.13,1:41:26.17,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是我猜他們知道我們的困境\NBut I wondered if they somehow knew of our privations.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.32,1:41:29.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}也許他們只是好奇\NMaybe they were just curious.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.14,1:42:19.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我保證過的 不是嗎\NI promised, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.58,1:42:28.71,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}天啊\NGod.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.96,1:42:34.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿 寶貝 你是誰啊\NHey, Sweetie! Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.15,1:42:37.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}菲比安\NPhebe Ann.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.10,1:42:42.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}菲比安·查斯\NPhebe Ann Chase.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.00,1:42:45.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他是你的父親\NIt's your Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.42,1:42:49.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}嘿 寶貝\NHey, Sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.00,1:42:56.43,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他是你的父親\NIt's your Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.27,1:43:15.51,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}當然還是有人找上他\NOf course they couldn't leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.78,1:43:18.72,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生和他的妻子往家走了不久\NMr. Chase and his wife had scarcely walked a block towards home
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.80,1:43:21.95,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他就被攔下來並帶回了海事辦公室\Nwhen he was stopped and made to return to the Maritime Office.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.41,1:43:26.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}生意上的事還有疑問\NThere were business matters still in question.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.12,1:43:41.78,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}對於這件事\NSo, to the matter...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.18,1:43:49.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}因為我們此次航線造成了巨大的人員和財產損失\NDue to the significant loss of life and property on our voyage,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.19,1:43:52.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}將會有一場聽證會\Nit seems there will be an inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.14,1:43:57.58,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}作為船長和大副 我們需要交待事實經過\NAnd, as Captain and first mate, we will be expected to give account of what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.03,1:43:59.36,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是的 當然\NYes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.42,1:44:04.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我就這件事和船主和我父親討論過\NAnd, having discussed this with the ship owners and... my father,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.11,1:44:08.69,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}顯然完全交待經過會有後果\Nit is clear that full disclosure will have ramifications...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.34,1:44:12.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}對整個行業有可怕的後果\Nterrible ramifications for whole industry.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.13,1:44:15.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一頭白鯨弄沉了埃塞克斯號\NThat a whale brought down the Essex.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.66,1:44:18.95,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但這是事實\NBut it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.11,1:44:30.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}如果保險商和投資人開始擔心\NIf the insurance houses and investors were to start worrying about...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.08,1:44:32.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}海怪把船弄沉\Nsea monsters sinking ships,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.30,1:44:36.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}水手們很難活下來\Nsailors drawing lots to survive...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.27,1:44:40.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們在石油行業 所有人\NWe are in the oil business... all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.50,1:44:47.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}在任何一個行業成功的機率一定要比失敗的風險要高\NAnd as in any business the probability of success must always be greater the risk incurred.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.79,1:44:50.66,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那麼 你有什麼建議 喬治\NSo, what are you suggesting, George?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.89,1:44:53.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你就說船擱淺了\NThat you say that the ship ran aground.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.27,1:44:56.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那是個謊言 並且說船員是淹死的\N- That's a lie. - And that the men that died drowned.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.41,1:44:58.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那也是個謊言\NThat's another lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.24,1:45:00.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}想想吧 他們會讓你當船長\NThink on it... they will make you captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.23,1:45:02.50,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個我是有書面保證的\NOh! That pledge I already have in writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.61,1:45:06.61,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個前提是你帶回一船的鯨油\NOnly on the condition you bring home a ship full of oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.87,1:45:09.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這麼做會確保你這件事\NThis way it's guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.75,1:45:12.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你會變成有錢人\NYou would be a wealthy man.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.18,1:45:16.48,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯不再是陸人的名字 而是有記錄的\NThe name Chase need no longer be a landsman's name, but an established name
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.51,1:45:20.03,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}屬於楠塔基特島偉大家族的名字\Nthat belongs among the great families of Nantucket.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.81,1:45:23.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你要我為了功名掩蓋發生的一切\NYou want me to whitewash what happened for profit?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.07,1:45:27.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們是要你務實些\NWe're asking you to be pragmatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.75,1:45:45.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號是被一頭白鯨撞沉的\NThe Essex was stoved by a white whale.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.04,1:45:48.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們倖存下來的在裝備不良的捕鯨船上\NAnd those of us that survived in ill-equipped whale boats
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.94,1:45:53.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}只能靠犯下罪孽才能存活\Nhad to commit abominations in order to survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.27,1:45:57.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我們回來後 又被指望傳播公然露骨的謊言\NAnd on our return, we're expected to spread barefaced lies,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.77,1:46:00.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}好讓你們這些楠塔基特島島船主們\Nso that you, the ship owners of Nantucket,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.38,1:46:04.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}賺錢晚上再睡得安穩覺嗎\Nmight line your pockets and sleep well at night?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.41,1:46:08.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我不會掩蓋真相\NWell, I will not embroil the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.93,1:46:10.76,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}喬治 你也不應該\NNor should you, George.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.27,1:46:32.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我最後一次見他\NThat last time I saw him...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.47,1:46:33.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}查斯先生 長官\NMr. Chase, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.32,1:46:37.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我說不出我想說的話\NI couldn't find the right words to say what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.74,1:46:40.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}湯姆斯\NThomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.01,1:46:42.78,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}也許我沒什麼想說的\NPerhaps there ARE no words.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.18,1:46:48.20,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我 我要去法爾茅斯了\NI'm... I'm gonna be on my way to Falmouth, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.33,1:46:52.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個\Nit's...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.12,1:46:55.43,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}那個 很榮幸 長官\Nit's... it's been an honor, Sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.75,1:46:57.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}能夠服務於您\Nto serve with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.83,1:47:03.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是我的榮幸 尼克森先生\NThe honor has been mine, Mr. Nickerson.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.82,1:47:22.54,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拿著\NTake it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.10,1:47:29.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}祝你好運 湯姆斯\NGood luck out there, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.11,1:47:31.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}謝謝 長官\NThank you, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.70,1:48:03.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}第二天喬治·波拉德被召喚到聽證會\NNext day George Pollard was called before the inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.53,1:48:10.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}先生們 船長喬治·波拉德\NGentlemen, Captain George Pollard.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.41,1:48:13.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}楠塔基特所有重要人物都在那兒\NAll the important men of Nantucket were there...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.96,1:48:17.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這是慣例\Nit was a formality.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.91,1:48:20.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}日安 船長 請坐\NGood day to you, Captain, please sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.88,1:48:27.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}事實是\NFor the record then.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.51,1:48:35.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}埃塞克斯號是在厄瓜多爾以西被一頭1200多米長的白鯨撞沉的\NThe Essex was stoved by a white whale 12 hundred meters west of Ecuador.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.20,1:48:38.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}就像歐文·查斯說的那樣\NIt was as if Owen Chase himself had spoken.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.90,1:48:42.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他告訴了他們真相\NHe told them the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.37,1:48:47.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}船長波拉德的良心發現了\NCap'n Pollard's conscience was clear...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.07,1:48:51.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但那場聽證會是個恥辱\Nbut the inquiry was a sham.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.02,1:48:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.51,1:49:01.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}至於那頭白鯨 他們再也沒有找到\Nover the white whale... they never found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.78,1:49:05.71,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他再一次出航但在夏威夷擱淺\NHe ran a second ship aground off of Hawaii...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.82,1:49:08.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}兩次詛咒\Ntwice cursed.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.63,1:49:11.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}再也沒有出航過\NNever sailed again.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.56,1:49:13.21,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}歐文·查斯\NAnd Owen Chase?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.31,1:49:16.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他說到做到\NHe was a man of his word.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.78,1:49:19.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他派了一艘船去了杜斯特島\NFirst, he sent a boat back to Ducie Island.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.82,1:49:22.66,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}花花公子已經死了\NMr. Joy had passed...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.92,1:49:26.43,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但是其他人居然還都活著\Nbut the other three were incredibly still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.28,1:49:30.55,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}然後呢\NAnd then?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.07,1:49:34.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}他帶著家人搬到了新貝德福德\NThen he packed up his family and moved to New Bedford...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.66,1:49:38.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}去重新開始生活\Nto start over...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.77,1:49:40.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}在一家商店\Nin a merchant...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.07,1:49:43.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}完成自己的人生旅程\Nsailing his own terms.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.68,1:49:56.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你用錢換到故事了 梅爾維爾先生\NWell, you certainly got your money's worth, Mr. Melville.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.40,1:49:58.79,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這二月的夜晚真是一年中最漫長的\NThese February nights are the longest of the year.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.08,1:50:02.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你們都可以休息了 我不行\N- Well, you can both rest now. - Leave me...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.45,1:50:05.32,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我還有一段時間不能休息\NI shall not be resting for some time.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.57,1:50:07.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}為什麼\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.72,1:50:12.89,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你得到了你的故事 情節都有了\NYa got your story there, and your plot is all there.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.94,1:50:16.67,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}也許我想要的不是情節\NMaybe it wasn't a plot I was after.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.82,1:50:18.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不是 那是什麼\NNo, what then?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.06,1:50:21.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你今晚給我的其他東西\NSomething else you've given me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.61,1:50:23.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是什麼\NWhat is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.70,1:50:28.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}敢於去別人不敢去的地方的勇氣\NThe courage to go where... one does not want to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.81,1:50:31.65,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}梅爾維爾先生\NMr. Melville,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.94,1:50:34.99,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你聽到的 我告訴你的\Nwhat you've heard, what I've told you,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.67,1:50:42.16,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}是否都會成為你書中的一部分\Nwill it all be of service to your book?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.25,1:50:46.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}這會是部虛構的小說 尼克森先生\NIt will be a work of fiction, Mr. Nickerson,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.00,1:50:49.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}受真實事件啟發\Ninspired by truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.04,1:50:54.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}但我不覺得我會用全部事實\Nbut I don't believe I'll feel the need to use all of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.40,1:51:04.73,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}謝謝 給\N- Thank you. - Here...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.21,1:51:06.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}拿著這個\Ntake that with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.48,1:51:08.83,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不 錢是給你的 我堅持\NNo, the money is for you, I insist.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.99,1:51:11.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我堅持你要收下\NI insist you keep it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.57,1:51:16.12,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我堅持這談話裏還是有一個人是清醒的\NAnd I insist that one person in this conversation is sober.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.27,1:51:29.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}該回馬薩諸塞州皮茨菲爾德了\NSo, it's back to Pittsfield, Massachusetts.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.82,1:51:32.38,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}祝你好運\NWell, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.49,1:51:34.75,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.19,1:51:39.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}你知道嗎\NYa know...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.95,1:51:43.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我聽說賓夕法尼亞州一個人最近在地上鑽了一個洞\NI heard a man from Pennsylvania drilled a hole in the ground recently,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.60,1:51:46.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}發現了油\Nand found oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.80,1:51:48.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}不會是真的吧\NThat can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.12,1:51:50.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}我也聽說過\NI heard it, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.44,1:51:55.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}地上的油\NOil from ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.57,1:51:59.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}真想不到\NFancy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.57,1:52:38.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}赫爾曼·梅爾維爾 1850年完成了他的小說
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.57,1:52:48.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}一年後白鯨記發表
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.57,1:52:58.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,280)\fscx50\fscy100}對於白鯨記納撒尼爾·霍桑盛讚它會成為美國偉大的作品
